msgstr "`Tutorial Odoo: eCommerce <https://www.odoo.com/slides/ecommerce-26>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/b2b_b2c.rst:3
msgid "B2B and B2C"
msgstr "B2B dan B2C"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/b2b_b2c.rst:5
msgid ""
"Odoo eCommerce is designed to fulfill the needs of both B2B and B2C "
"companies. It allows you to configure :doc:`prices <products/prices>`, "
"manage :doc:`access <customer_accounts>` for specific customers, "
"and :ref:`customize the website <ecommerce/b2b_b2c/multiple-websites>` to "
"support B2B, B2C, or both business models."
msgstr ""
"Odoo eCommerce dirancang untuk memenuhi kebutuhan perusahaan B2B maupun B2C. "
"Ini memungkinkan Anda untuk mengkonfigurasi :doc:`harga <products/prices>`, "
"mengelola :doc:`akses <customer_accounts>` untuk pelanggan tertentu, dan "
":ref:`menyesuaikan website <ecommerce/b2b_b2c/multiple-websites>` untuk "
"mendukung model bisnis B2B, B2C, atau keduanya."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/b2b_b2c.rst:13
#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:3
msgid "Prices"
msgstr "Harga"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/b2b_b2c.rst:15
msgid ""
"While B2C businesses sell directly to the end consumer with a :ref:`tax-"
"included <ecommerce-price-management-tax-display>` price, B2B businesses "
"usually :ref:`exclude taxes <ecommerce-price-management-tax-display>` and "
"may even prefer to hide prices altogether, showcasing only their products "
"instead. To configure a B2B-specific ecommerce shop, make sure the :ref:`Tax-"
"Excluded <ecommerce/prices/taxes>` option is enabled, and complete the "
"configuration to :ref:`hide the pricing <ecommerce/prices/hide-prices>`."
msgstr ""
"Sementara bisnis B2C menjual langsung ke konsumen akhir dengan harga "
":ref:`sudah termasuk pajak <ecommerce-price-management-tax-display>`, bisnis "
"B2B biasanya :ref:`tidak termasuk pajak <ecommerce-price-management-tax-"
"display>` dan bahkan mungkin lebih suka menyembunyikan harga sama sekali, "
"hanya menampilkan produk mereka. Untuk mengonfigurasi toko ecommerce khusus "
"B2B, pastikan opsi :ref:`Tidak Termasuk Pajak <ecommerce/prices/taxes>` "
"diaktifkan, dan selesaikan konfigurasi untuk :ref:`menyembunyikan harga "
"<ecommerce/prices/hide-prices>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/b2b_b2c.rst:24
msgid ""
"To make sure that only customers with an :ref:`account and granted access "
"<ecommerce/customer_accounts/account-creation>` can see the prices, go "
"to :menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce --> Customers`, click the :icon:`fa-"
"caret-down` :guilabel:`(dropdown)` icon from the search bar, and select "
"the :guilabel:`Archived` filter. Then click the :guilabel:`Public user` "
"card, go to the :guilabel:`Sales & Purchase` tab, and add the zero-priced "
"pricelist configured to :ref:`cover all countries <ecommerce/prices/country-"
"groups>`. Keep the :guilabel:`Public User` contact :guilabel:`Archived` at "
"all times. Website visitors now see the products without prices, while only "
"customers with an :ref:`account invitation <ecommerce/customer_accounts/"
"account-creation>` and an assigned :ref:`pricelist <ecommerce/prices/"
"pricelists>` can view the pricing in the customer portal."
msgstr ""
"Untuk memastikan bahwa hanya pelanggan dengan :ref:`akun dan akses yang "
"diberikan <ecommerce/customer_accounts/account-creation>` yang dapat melihat "
"harga, buka :menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce --> Customers`, klik ikon "
":icon:`fa-caret-down` :guilabel:`(dropdown)` dari bilah pencarian, dan pilih "
"filter :guilabel:`Archived`. Kemudian klik kartu :guilabel:`Public user`, "
"buka tab :guilabel:`Sales & Purchase`, dan tambahkan daftar harga berharga "
"nol yang dikonfigurasi untuk :ref:`mencakup semua negara <ecommerce/prices/"
"country-groups>`. Selalu biarkan kontak :guilabel:`Public User` dalam status "
":guilabel:`Archived`. Pengunjung website sekarang melihat produk tanpa "
"harga, sementara hanya pelanggan dengan :ref:`undangan akun <ecommerce/"
"customer_accounts/account-creation>` dan :ref:`daftar harga <ecommerce/"
"prices/pricelists>` yang ditetapkan dapat melihat harga di portal pelanggan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/b2b_b2c.rst:36
msgid ":doc:`/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/B2B_B2C`"
msgstr ":doc:`/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/B2B_B2C`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/b2b_b2c.rst:37
msgid ":ref:`Discounts <ecommerce/prices/discounts>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Diskon <ecommerce/prices/discounts>`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/b2b_b2c.rst:40
msgid "Access request"
msgstr "Permintaan akses"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/b2b_b2c.rst:42
msgid ""
"When running a B2B business, you usually :ref:`hide the pricing <ecommerce/"
"b2b_b2c/prices>` on the web shop and make it available for :ref:`logged-in "
"users <ecommerce/customer_accounts/shop-access>` only. To prevent anyone "
"from signing up freely, set the :ref:`Customer Account <ecommerce/"
"customer_accounts/account-creation>` setting option to :guilabel:`On "
"invitation`. To create a page where customers request access, open "
"the :doc:`website editor <../website/web_design>`, :ref:`create a form "
"<website/building_blocks/form>`, customize it, and in the :guilabel:`Action` "
"field, select :guilabel:`Create a customer`."
msgstr ""
"Saat menjalankan bisnis B2B, Anda biasanya :ref:`menyembunyikan harga "
"<ecommerce/b2b_b2c/prices>` di toko web dan menyediakannya hanya untuk "
":ref:`pengguna yang login <ecommerce/customer_accounts/shop-access>`. Untuk "
"mencegah siapa pun mendaftar secara bebas, setel opsi pengaturan :ref:`Akun "
"Pelanggan <ecommerce/customer_accounts/account-creation>` ke :guilabel:`Atas "
"undangan`. Untuk membuat halaman di mana pelanggan meminta akses, buka "
":doc:`editor website <../website/web_design>`, :ref:`buat formulir <website/"
"building_blocks/form>`, sesuaikan, dan di kolom :guilabel:`Tindakan`, pilih "
":guilabel:`Buat pelanggan`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/b2b_b2c.rst:51
msgid ""
"You can assign tags created on a contact form under :menuselection:`Website "
"--> Configuration --> Customers` to identify what kind of customers have "
"submitted the form. To do so, select a field in the form while "
"in :guilabel:`Edit` mode, click the :guilabel:`+ Field` button under "
"the :guilabel:`Customize` tab, and set the field's :guilabel:`Type` "
"to :guilabel:`Tags`. Toggle the tags that should be automatically assigned "
"when a customer fills in the form and set the field's :guilabel:`Visibility` "
"to :guilabel:`Hidden`."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat menetapkan tag yang dibuat pada formulir kontak di "
":menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Customers` untuk "
"mengidentifikasi jenis pelanggan yang telah mengirimkan formulir. Untuk "
"melakukannya, pilih kolom dalam formulir saat dalam mode :guilabel:`Edit`, "
"klik tombol :guilabel:`+ Field` di bawah tab :guilabel:`Customize`, dan "
"setel :guilabel:`Type` kolom ke :guilabel:`Tags`. Aktifkan tag yang harus "
"secara otomatis ditetapkan ketika pelanggan mengisi formulir dan setel "
":guilabel:`Visibility` kolom ke :guilabel:`Hidden`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/b2b_b2c.rst:58
msgid ""
"When a customer submits the form, a new contact is automatically created in "
"the database. The contact is assigned the first pricelist from the list of "
"available pricelists, and, if applicable, the specified tags."
msgstr ""
"Ketika pelanggan mengirimkan formulir, kontak baru secara otomatis dibuat di "
"database. Kontak tersebut ditetapkan daftar harga pertama dari daftar daftar "
"harga yang tersedia, dan, jika berlaku, tag yang ditentukan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/b2b_b2c.rst:62
msgid ""
"Submitted requests can be found under the :menuselection:`Website --> "
"eCommerce --> Customers`. Select the customer you want to :ref:`grant portal "
"access <ecommerce/customer_accounts/grant-access>` to. Once done, the "
"selected customer is able to view the B2B prices and products. Make sure the "
"correct pricelist is assigned to their contact form."
msgstr ""
"Permintaan yang dikirimkan dapat ditemukan di :menuselection:`Website --> "
"eCommerce --> Customers`. Pilih pelanggan yang ingin Anda :ref:`berikan "
"akses portal <ecommerce/customer_accounts/grant-access>`. Setelah selesai, "
"pelanggan yang dipilih dapat melihat harga dan produk B2B. Pastikan daftar "
"harga yang benar ditetapkan ke formulir kontak mereka."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/b2b_b2c.rst:69
msgid ""
"It is also possible to hide the entire shop from the public using "
"the :ref:`Ecommerce Access <ecommerce/customer_accounts/shop-access>` "
"setting and only make it available for logged-in customers."
msgstr ""
"Dimungkinkan juga untuk menyembunyikan seluruh toko dari publik menggunakan "
"pengaturan :ref:`Ecommerce Access <ecommerce/customer_accounts/shop-access>` "
"dan hanya menyediakannya untuk pelanggan yang sudah login."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/b2b_b2c.rst:72
msgid ""
"Configure the :ref:`checkout policy <ecommerce/customer_accounts/checkout-"
"access>` to allow/disallow guest checkout for B2C businesses."
msgstr ""
"Konfigurasikan :ref:`kebijakan checkout <ecommerce/customer_accounts/"
"checkout-access>` untuk mengizinkan/melarang checkout tamu untuk bisnis B2C."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/b2b_b2c.rst:74
msgid ""
"Enable the :ref:`Shared Customer Accounts <ecommerce/customer_accounts/"
"multiple-websites>` feature to allow customers to use the same account "
"on :ref:`all <ecommerce/b2b_b2c/multiple-websites>` your websites."
msgstr ""
"Aktifkan fitur :ref:`Shared Customer Accounts <ecommerce/customer_accounts/"
"multiple-websites>` untuk memungkinkan pelanggan menggunakan akun yang sama "
"di :ref:`semua <ecommerce/b2b_b2c/multiple-websites>` website Anda."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/b2b_b2c.rst:79
msgid ":doc:`customer_accounts`"
msgstr ":doc:`customer_accounts`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/b2b_b2c.rst:84
#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:3
msgid "Multiple websites"
msgstr "Beberapa website"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/b2b_b2c.rst:86
msgid ""
"Settings are website-specific, which means it is possible to configure "
"different behaviors for each website. For example, you can set up a B2C "
"website that allows :ref:`guest checkout <ecommerce/customer_accounts/"
"checkout-access>` and displays :ref:`tax-included prices <ecommerce-price-"
"management-tax-display>`, and a B2B website that requires :ref:`sign-in "
"<ecommerce/customer_accounts/checkout-access>` and shows :ref:`tax-excluded "
"prices <ecommerce-price-management-tax-display>`. However, "
"each :ref:`pricelist <ecommerce/prices/pricelists>` can only be assigned to "
"one website at a time. If you want to use the same pricelist on several "
"websites, duplicate the pricelist and assign each copy to its corresponding "
"website."
msgstr ""
"Pengaturan bersifat spesifik untuk website, yang berarti dimungkinkan untuk "
"mengonfigurasi perilaku yang berbeda untuk setiap website. Misalnya, Anda "
"dapat menyiapkan website B2C yang mengizinkan :ref:`checkout tamu <ecommerce/"
"customer_accounts/checkout-access>` dan menampilkan :ref:`harga termasuk "
"pajak <ecommerce-price-management-tax-display>`, dan website B2B yang "
"memerlukan :ref:`sign-in <ecommerce/customer_accounts/checkout-access>` dan "
"menampilkan :ref:`harga belum termasuk pajak <ecommerce-price-management-tax-"
"display>`. Namun, setiap :ref:`daftar harga <ecommerce/prices/pricelists>` "
"hanya dapat ditetapkan ke satu website pada satu waktu. Jika Anda ingin "
"menggunakan daftar harga yang sama di beberapa website, duplikasikan daftar "
"harga dan tetapkan setiap salinan ke website yang sesuai."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/b2b_b2c.rst:97
msgid ""
"If you are running a B2B and B2C business, we *strongly* recommend to create "
"two :doc:`separate websites <../website/configuration/multi_website>` and "
"assign a :ref:`zero-priced pricelist <ecommerce/b2b_b2c/prices>` to the B2B "
"website and a regular pricelist to the B2C website. In case, you prefer "
"using a single website, configure it using :ref:`country groups <ecommerce/"
"prices/country-groups>` and assigning :ref:`pricelists <ecommerce/prices/"
"pricelists>` to customers, and deactivate the :ref:`Selectable <ecommerce/"
"prices/selectable-pricelists>` option."
msgstr ""
"Jika Anda menjalankan bisnis B2B dan B2C, kami *sangat* merekomendasikan "
"untuk membuat dua :doc:`website terpisah <../website/configuration/"
"multi_website>` dan menetapkan :ref:`pricelist harga nol <ecommerce/b2b_b2c/"
"prices>` ke website B2B dan pricelist reguler ke website B2C. Jika Anda "
"lebih suka menggunakan satu website, konfigurasikan menggunakan :ref:`grup "
"negara <ecommerce/prices/country-groups>` dan menetapkan :ref:`pricelist "
"<ecommerce/prices/pricelists>` ke pelanggan, dan nonaktifkan opsi "
":ref:`Selectable <ecommerce/prices/selectable-pricelists>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/b2b_b2c.rst:106
#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:258
msgid "Additional features"
msgstr "Fitur tambahan"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/b2b_b2c.rst:109
msgid "Invoice"
msgstr "Faktur"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/b2b_b2c.rst:111
msgid ""
"Depending on the type of business (B2B or B2C), you might want to issue an "
"invoice. An invoice can either be generated automatically (for B2B) or on "
"demand of the customer (for B2C). This process can be automated if (and "
"when) the online payment is :ref:`confirmed <handling/sales>`. To automate "
"invoicing, enable the :ref:`Automatic Invoice <handling/legal>` setting. If "
"this feature has not been enabled, the customer only receives an order "
"confirmation."
msgstr ""
"Tergantung pada jenis bisnis (B2B atau B2C), Anda mungkin ingin menerbitkan "
"invoice. Invoice dapat dibuat secara otomatis (untuk B2B) atau atas "
"permintaan pelanggan (untuk B2C). Proses ini dapat diotomatisasi jika (dan "
"ketika) pembayaran online :ref:`dikonfirmasi <handling/sales>`. Untuk "
"mengotomatisasi penagihan, aktifkan pengaturan :ref:`Automatic Invoice "
"<handling/legal>`. Jika fitur ini belum diaktifkan, pelanggan hanya menerima "
"konfirmasi pesanan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/b2b_b2c.rst:120
msgid "B2B fields at checkout"
msgstr "Kolom B2B di checkout"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/b2b_b2c.rst:122
msgid ""
"Use the :guilabel:`Show B2B fields` toggle in the :doc:`website editor <../"
"website/web_design>` to display B2B-specific additional fields "
"like :guilabel:`VAT` or :guilabel:`Company Name` during the :ref:`delivery "
"<ecommerce/checkout/delivery>` step."
msgstr ""
"Gunakan toggle :guilabel:`Show B2B fields` di :doc:`editor website <../"
"website/web_design>` untuk menampilkan kolom tambahan khusus B2B seperti "
":guilabel:`VAT` atau :guilabel:`Company Name` selama langkah :ref:`delivery "
"<ecommerce/checkout/delivery>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:3
msgid "Ordering and checkout"
msgstr "Pemesanan dan checkout"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:5
msgid ""
"Odoo eCommerce provides several options to organize the ordering and "
"checkout process. It offers different :ref:`order button <ecommerce/checkout/"
"order-buttons>` options and sequential :ref:`checkout steps <ecommerce/"
"checkout/steps>`, some of which support additional features. The related "
"buttons and checkout pages can be customized using the website editor."
msgstr ""
"Odoo eCommerce menyediakan beberapa opsi untuk mengatur proses pemesanan dan "
"checkout. Aplikasi ini menawarkan berbagai opsi :ref:`tombol pesan "
"<ecommerce/checkout/order-buttons>` dan :ref:`langkah checkout <ecommerce/"
"checkout/steps>` berurutan, beberapa di antaranya mendukung fitur tambahan. "
"Tombol dan halaman checkout terkait dapat dikustomisasi menggunakan editor "
"website."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:13
msgid "Order buttons"
msgstr "Tombol pemesanan"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:15
msgid "To customize the ordering process in Odoo eCommerce, you can:"
msgstr "Untuk menyesuaikan proses pemesanan di Odoo eCommerce, Anda dapat:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:17
msgid ""
"change the :ref:`Add to Cart <ecommerce/checkout/add-to-cart>` button's "
"behavior,"
msgstr ""
"ubah perilaku tombol :ref:`Add to Cart <ecommerce/checkout/add-to-cart>`,"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:18
msgid ""
"replace it with a :ref:`customized <ecommerce/checkout/prevent-sale>` button,"
msgstr ""
"ganti dengan tombol yang :ref:`dikustomisasi <ecommerce/checkout/prevent-"
"sale>`,"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:19
msgid "add a :ref:`Buy now <ecommerce/checkout/buy-now>` button, and"
msgstr "tambahkan tombol :ref:`Buy now <ecommerce/checkout/buy-now>`, dan"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:20
msgid ""
"add an :ref:`Order again <ecommerce/checkout/re-order>` button to the "
"customer portal."
msgstr ""
"tambahkan tombol :ref:`Order again <ecommerce/checkout/re-order>` ke portal "
"pelanggan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:25
msgid "Add to cart options"
msgstr "Opsi tambahkan ke keranjang"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:28
msgid "Default add to cart behavior"
msgstr "Perilaku tambahkan ke keranjang default"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:30
msgid ""
"When clicking the :guilabel:`Add to cart` button, different actions can be "
"triggered. To configure them, go to :menuselection:`Website --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`, scroll down to the :guilabel:`Shop - Checkout "
"Process` section, and select one of the following options:"
msgstr ""
"Saat mengklik tombol :guilabel:`Add to cart`, berbagai tindakan dapat "
"dipicu. Untuk mengonfigurasinya, buka :menuselection:`Website --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`, gulir ke bawah ke bagian :guilabel:`Shop - "
"Checkout Process`, dan pilih salah satu opsi berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:34
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Stay on Product Page`: The customer remains on the product's page."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Stay on Product Page`: Pelanggan tetap berada di halaman produk."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:35
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Go to cart`: The customer is immediately redirected to the cart."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Go to cart`: Pelanggan langsung diarahkan ke keranjang."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:36
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Let the user decide (dialog)`: The customer can choose if they "
"want to go to the cart (:guilabel:`Proceed to Checkout`) or if they prefer "
"to stay on the product page (:guilabel:`Continue Shopping`)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Let the user decide (dialog)`: Pelanggan dapat memilih apakah "
"mereka ingin pergi ke keranjang (:guilabel:`Proceed to Checkout`) atau jika "
"mereka lebih suka tetap di halaman produk (:guilabel:`Continue Shopping`)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:41
msgid ""
"This dialog box always appears regardless of the configuration to "
"suggest :doc:`optional products <products/cross_upselling>`, if any."
msgstr ""
"Kotak dialog ini selalu muncul terlepas dari konfigurasi untuk menyarankan "
":doc:`produk opsional <products/cross_upselling>`, jika ada."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:47
msgid "Button customization"
msgstr "Kustomisasi tombol"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:49
msgid ""
"You can replace the :guilabel:`Add to Cart` button with a :guilabel:`Contact "
"Us` button, which redirects users to the default contact form."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat mengganti tombol :guilabel:`Tambahkan ke Keranjang` dengan tombol "
":guilabel:`Hubungi Kami`, yang mengarahkan pengguna ke formulir kontak "
"default."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:53
msgid ""
"Removing the ability to add products to the cart is often used by businesses "
"that want to display an online catalog but cannot share prices publicly "
"(e.g., to offer custom or variable pricing)."
msgstr ""
"Menghapus kemampuan untuk menambahkan produk ke keranjang sering digunakan "
"oleh bisnis yang ingin menampilkan katalog online tetapi tidak dapat "
"membagikan harga secara publik (misalnya, untuk menawarkan harga kustom atau "
"variabel)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:56
msgid ""
"To display the :guilabel:`Contact Us` button and a note saying `Not "
"Available For Sale` , you need to :ref:`hide your prices <ecommerce/prices/"
"hide-prices>` on your product page."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:None
msgid "Contact us button on product page"
msgstr "Tombol hubungi kami di halaman produk"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:63
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Contact Us` button label, URL, and the *Not Available For "
"Sale* text beneath the product title and description can be modified on the "
"product's page while in :guilabel:`Edit` mode."
msgstr ""
"Label tombol :guilabel:`Hubungi Kami`, URL, dan teks *Tidak Tersedia untuk "
"Dijual* di bawah judul dan deskripsi produk dapat dimodifikasi pada halaman "
"produk saat dalam mode :guilabel:`Edit`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:68
msgid "Additional add to cart buttons"
msgstr "Tombol tambahan tambahkan ke keranjang"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:70
msgid ""
"You can add additional :guilabel:`Add to Cart` buttons and link them to "
"specific products on any website page."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat menambahkan tombol :guilabel:`Tambahkan ke Keranjang` tambahan "
"dan menghubungkannya ke produk tertentu di halaman website mana pun."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:73
msgid ""
"To add them, open the website editor and place the :guilabel:`Add to Cart "
"Button` inner content building block. Once placed, click the button, scroll "
"to the :guilabel:`Add to Cart Button` section, and configure the following:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk menambahkannya, buka editor website dan tempatkan blok konten dalam "
":guilabel:`Add to Cart Button`. Setelah ditempatkan, klik tombol tersebut, "
"gulir ke bagian :guilabel:`Add to Cart Button`, dan konfigurasikan hal "
"berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:77
msgid ":guilabel:`Product`: Select the product to link the button with."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Produk`: Pilih produk untuk dihubungkan dengan tombol."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:78
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Action`: Choose if it should be an :guilabel:`Add to Cart` "
"or :ref:`Buy Now <ecommerce/checkout/buy-now>` button."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Action`: Pilih apakah harus berupa tombol :guilabel:`Add to Cart` "
"atau :ref:`Buy Now <ecommerce/checkout/buy-now>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:82
msgid ""
"If the product has variants, either choose one or leave the option "
"on :guilabel:`Visitor's Choice`, which prompts the customer to select a "
"variant and then to :guilabel:`Proceed to Checkout` or :guilabel:`Continue "
"Shopping`."
msgstr ""
"Jika produk memiliki varian, pilih salah satu atau biarkan opsi pada "
":guilabel:`Visitor's Choice`, yang meminta pelanggan untuk memilih varian "
"kemudian :guilabel:`Proceed to Checkout` atau :guilabel:`Continue Shopping`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:85
msgid ""
"The default :guilabel:`Add to Cart` button does not offer those options, but "
"its label can be changed."
msgstr ""
"Tombol :guilabel:`Add to Cart` default tidak menawarkan opsi tersebut, "
"tetapi labelnya dapat diubah."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:89
msgid ""
"While in :guilabel:`Edit` mode, it is also possible to show or hide "
"the :icon:`fa-shopping-cart` (:guilabel:`cart`) icon in the page's header. "
"Click the header and then the :icon:`fa-shopping-cart` (:guilabel:`cart`) "
"button next to the :guilabel:`Show Empty` option under "
"the :guilabel:`Customize` tab."
msgstr ""
"Saat dalam mode :guilabel:`Edit`, dimungkinkan juga untuk menampilkan atau "
"menyembunyikan ikon :icon:`fa-shopping-cart` (:guilabel:`cart`) di header "
"halaman. Klik header kemudian tombol :icon:`fa-shopping-cart` "
"(:guilabel:`cart`) di sebelah opsi :guilabel:`Show Empty` di bawah tab "
":guilabel:`Customize`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:97
msgid "Buy now"
msgstr "Beli sekarang"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:99
msgid ""
"To let customers choose to go to the :ref:`review order <ecommerce/checkout/"
"review_order>` step directly, you can add an additional :guilabel:`Buy now` "
"button. To do so, go to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> "
"Settings`. Under the :guilabel:`Shop - Checkout Process` section, tick "
"the :guilabel:`Buy Now` feature."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membiarkan pelanggan memilih langsung ke tahap :ref:`review order "
"<ecommerce/checkout/review_order>`, Anda dapat menambahkan tombol "
":guilabel:`Buy now` tambahan. Untuk melakukannya, buka "
":menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings`. Di bawah bagian "
":guilabel:`Shop - Checkout Process`, centang fitur :guilabel:`Buy Now`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:105
msgid ""
"Alternatively, enable the feature by going to any product's page while "
"in :guilabel:`Edit` mode and, in the :guilabel:`Customize` tab, clicking "
"the :icon:`fa-bolt` :guilabel:`Buy Now` button next to the :guilabel:`Cart` "
"options."
msgstr ""
"Atau, aktifkan fitur tersebut dengan membuka halaman produk mana pun saat "
"dalam mode :guilabel:`Edit` dan, di tab :guilabel:`Customize`, klik tombol "
":icon:`fa-bolt` :guilabel:`Buy Now` di sebelah opsi :guilabel:`Cart`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:None
msgid "Buy now button"
msgstr "Tombol beli sekarang"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:115
msgid "Re-order from portal"
msgstr "Pesan ulang dari portal"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:117
msgid ""
"You can let customers re-order items from previous sales orders from their "
"customer portal using the :guilabel:`Order Again` button. To add it, go "
"to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings`. Under "
"the :guilabel:`Shop - Checkout Process` section, tick the :guilabel:`Re-"
"order From Portal` feature."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat membiarkan pelanggan memesan ulang item dari sales order "
"sebelumnya dari portal pelanggan mereka menggunakan tombol :guilabel:`Order "
"Again`. Untuk menambahkannya, buka :menuselection:`Website --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`. Di bawah bagian :guilabel:`Shop - Checkout "
"Process`, centang fitur :guilabel:`Re-order From Portal`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:None
msgid "Re-order button"
msgstr "Tombol pesan ulang"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:128
msgid "Checkout steps"
msgstr "Langkah checkout"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:130
msgid ""
"During the checkout process, customers are taken through the following steps:"
msgstr "Selama proses checkout, pelanggan melalui langkah-langkah berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:132
msgid ":ref:`Review order <ecommerce/checkout/review_order>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Review order <ecommerce/checkout/review_order>`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:133
msgid ":ref:`Delivery <ecommerce/checkout/delivery>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Delivery <ecommerce/checkout/delivery>`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:134
msgid ":ref:`Extra info (if enabled) <ecommerce/checkout/extra_step>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Extra info (if enabled) <ecommerce/checkout/extra_step>`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:135
msgid ":ref:`Payment <ecommerce/checkout/payment>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Pembayaran <ecommerce/checkout/payment>`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:136
msgid ":ref:`Order confirmation <ecommerce/checkout/order_confirmation>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Konfirmasi pesanan <ecommerce/checkout/order_confirmation>`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:140
msgid ""
"Each step can be customized using the website editor by "
"adding :doc:`building blocks <../website/web_design/building_blocks>` or "
"opening the :guilabel:`Customize` tab to enable various checkout options."
msgstr ""
"Setiap langkah dapat disesuaikan menggunakan editor website dengan "
"menambahkan :doc:`building blocks <../website/web_design/building_blocks>` "
"atau membuka tab :guilabel:`Customize` untuk mengaktifkan berbagai opsi "
"checkout."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:145
msgid "Content added through building blocks is **specific** to each step."
msgstr ""
"Konten yang ditambahkan melalui blok pembangunan **spesifik** untuk setiap "
"langkah."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:148
msgid ""
"Restrict access to the :ref:`shop <ecommerce/customer_accounts/shop-access>` "
"and :ref:`checkout <ecommerce/customer_accounts/checkout-access>` for "
"specific customers, e.g., in a :doc:`B2B <b2b_b2c>` business setup."
msgstr ""
"Batasi akses ke :ref:`shop <ecommerce/customer_accounts/shop-access>` dan "
":ref:`checkout <ecommerce/customer_accounts/checkout-access>` untuk "
"pelanggan tertentu, misalnya dalam pengaturan bisnis :doc:`B2B <b2b_b2c>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:155
msgid "Review order"
msgstr "Tinjau pesanan"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:157
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Review Order` step allows customers to see the items they "
"added to their cart, adjust quantities, or :guilabel:`Remove` products. "
"Information related to the product prices and taxes applied are also "
"displayed. Customers can then click the :guilabel:`Checkout` button to "
"continue to the :ref:`Delivery <ecommerce/checkout/delivery>` step."
msgstr ""
"Langkah :guilabel:`Tinjau Pesanan` memungkinkan pelanggan untuk melihat item "
"yang mereka tambahkan ke keranjang, menyesuaikan jumlah, atau "
":guilabel:`Hapus` produk. Informasi terkait harga produk dan pajak yang "
"diterapkan juga ditampilkan. Pelanggan kemudian dapat mengklik tombol "
":guilabel:`Checkout` untuk melanjutkan ke langkah :ref:`Pengiriman "
"<ecommerce/checkout/delivery>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:162
msgid ""
"Open the website editor to :ref:`enable <ecommerce/checkout/"
"customize_steps>` checkout options such as:"
msgstr ""
"Buka editor website untuk :ref:`mengaktifkan <ecommerce/checkout/"
"customize_steps>` opsi checkout seperti:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:165
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Suggested Accessories`: to showcase :ref:`accessory products "
"<ecommerce/cross_upselling/accessory>`;"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Aksesori yang Disarankan`: untuk menampilkan :ref:`produk "
"aksesori <ecommerce/cross_upselling/accessory>`;"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:167
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Promo Code`: to allow customers to redeem :ref:`gift cards "
"<ewallet_gift/gift-cards>` or apply :doc:`discount codes <../../sales/sales/"
"products_prices/loyalty_discount>`;"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Kode Promo`: untuk memungkinkan pelanggan menukarkan :ref:`kartu "
"hadiah <ewallet_gift/gift-cards>` atau menerapkan :doc:`kode diskon <../../"
"sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount>`;"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:169
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Add to Wishlist`: :ref:`Enable wishlists <ecommerce/products/"
"wishlists>` to allow signed-in users to remove a product from their cart and "
"add it to their wishlist using the :guilabel:`Save for later` option."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Add to Wishlist`: :ref:`Enable wishlists <ecommerce/products/"
"wishlists>` untuk memungkinkan pengguna yang sudah masuk menghapus produk "
"dari keranjang mereka dan menambahkannya ke wishlist menggunakan opsi "
":guilabel:`Save for later`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:174
msgid ""
"If a :doc:`fiscal position <../../finance/accounting/taxes/"
"fiscal_positions>` is detected automatically, the product tax is determined "
"based on the customer's IP address."
msgstr ""
"Jika :doc:`posisi fiskal <../../finance/accounting/taxes/fiscal_positions>` "
"terdeteksi secara otomatis, pajak produk ditentukan berdasarkan alamat IP "
"pelanggan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:176
msgid ""
"If the installed :doc:`payment provider <../../finance/payment_providers>` "
"supports :ref:`express checkout <payment_providers/express_checkout>`, a "
"dedicated button is displayed, allowing customers to go straight from the "
"cart to the confirmation page without filling out the contact form."
msgstr ""
"Jika :doc:`penyedia pembayaran <../../finance/payment_providers>` yang "
"terpasang mendukung :ref:`checkout ekspres <payment_providers/"
"express_checkout>`, tombol khusus ditampilkan, memungkinkan pelanggan "
"langsung dari keranjang ke halaman konfirmasi tanpa mengisi formulir kontak."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:184
#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:3
msgid "Delivery"
msgstr "Pengiriman"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:186
msgid "Once they have reviewed their order:"
msgstr "Setelah mereka meninjau pesanan mereka:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:188
msgid ""
"Unsigned-in customers are prompted to :guilabel:`Sign in` or enter "
"their :guilabel:`Email address`, along with their delivery address and phone "
"details;"
msgstr ""
"Pelanggan yang belum masuk diminta untuk :guilabel:`Masuk` atau memasukkan "
":guilabel:`Alamat Email` mereka, beserta alamat pengiriman dan detail "
"telepon;"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:190
msgid ""
"Signed-in customers can select the appropriate :guilabel:`Delivery address`."
msgstr ""
"Pelanggan yang sudah masuk dapat memilih :guilabel:`Alamat Pengiriman` yang "
"sesuai."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:192
msgid ""
"They can then :doc:`choose a delivery method <shipping>`, select or enter "
"their :guilabel:`Billing Address` (or toggle the :guilabel:`Same as delivery "
"address` switch if the billing and delivery addresses are identical), and "
"click :guilabel:`Confirm` to proceed to the next step."
msgstr ""
"Mereka kemudian dapat :doc:`memilih metode pengiriman <shipping>`, memilih "
"atau memasukkan :guilabel:`Alamat Penagihan` mereka (atau mengaktifkan "
"tombol :guilabel:`Sama dengan alamat pengiriman` jika alamat penagihan dan "
"pengiriman identik), dan klik :guilabel:`Konfirmasi` untuk melanjutkan ke "
"langkah berikutnya."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:197
msgid ""
"For B2B customers, you can also :ref:`enable <ecommerce/checkout/"
"customize_steps>` optional :ref:`B2B fields <ecommerce/b2b_b2c/b2b-fields>` "
"in the website editor."
msgstr ""
"Untuk pelanggan B2B, Anda juga dapat :ref:`mengaktifkan <ecommerce/checkout/"
"customize_steps>` :ref:`kolom B2B <ecommerce/b2b_b2c/b2b-fields>` opsional "
"di editor website."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:199
msgid ""
"You can add a checkbox for users without an account to sign up for a "
"newsletter. To do so, go to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> "
"Settings`. Under the :guilabel:`Shop - Checkout Process` section, enable "
"the :guilabel:`Newsletter` feature and select a :guilabel:`Newsletter List`."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat menambahkan kotak centang bagi pengguna tanpa akun untuk "
"mendaftar buletin. Untuk melakukannya, buka :menuselection:`Website --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`. Di bagian :guilabel:`Shop - Checkout Process`, "
"aktifkan fitur :guilabel:`Newsletter` dan pilih :guilabel:`Newsletter List`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:207
msgid "Extra info"
msgstr "Info ekstra"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:209
msgid ""
"You can add an :guilabel:`Extra Info` step in the checkout process to "
"collect additional customer information through an online form, which is "
"then included in the :ref:`sales order <handling/sales>`. To do "
"so, :ref:`enable <ecommerce/checkout/customize_steps>` the :guilabel:`Extra "
"Step` option in the website editor. The form can be :ref:`customized "
"<website/building_blocks/form>` as needed."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat menambahkan langkah :guilabel:`Info Tambahan` dalam proses "
"checkout untuk mengumpulkan informasi pelanggan tambahan melalui formulir "
"online, yang kemudian disertakan dalam :ref:`sales order <handling/sales>`. "
"Untuk melakukannya, :ref:`aktifkan <ecommerce/checkout/customize_steps>` "
"opsi :guilabel:`Extra Step` di editor website. Formulir dapat "
":ref:`disesuaikan <website/building_blocks/form>` sesuai kebutuhan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:216
msgid ""
"Alternatively, go to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> "
"Settings`, scroll to the :guilabel:`Shop - Checkout Process` section, "
"enable :guilabel:`Extra Step During Checkout`, and click :guilabel:`Save`. "
"Click :icon:`fa-arrow-right` :guilabel:`Configure Form` to customize it."
msgstr ""
"Atau, buka :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings`, gulir ke "
"bagian :guilabel:`Shop - Checkout Process`, aktifkan :guilabel:`Extra Step "
"During Checkout`, dan klik :guilabel:`Save`. Klik :icon:`fa-arrow-right` "
":guilabel:`Configure Form` untuk menyesuaikannya."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:223
msgid "Payment"
msgstr "Pembayaran"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:225
msgid ""
"At the :guilabel:`Payment` step, customers :guilabel:`Choose a payment "
"method`, enter their payment details, and click :guilabel:`Pay now`."
msgstr ""
"Pada langkah :guilabel:`Pembayaran`, pelanggan :guilabel:`Pilih metode "
"pembayaran`, masukkan detail pembayaran mereka, dan klik :guilabel:`Bayar "
"sekarang`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:228
msgid ""
"You can require customers to agree to your :doc:`terms and conditions <../../"
"finance/accounting/customer_invoices/terms_conditions>` before payment. "
"To :ref:`enable <ecommerce/checkout/customize_steps>` this option, go to the "
"website editor and toggle the :guilabel:`Accept Terms & Conditions` feature."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat mewajibkan pelanggan untuk menyetujui :doc:`syarat dan ketentuan "
"<../../finance/accounting/customer_invoices/terms_conditions>` Anda sebelum "
"pembayaran. Untuk :ref:`mengaktifkan <ecommerce/checkout/customize_steps>` "
"opsi ini, buka editor website dan aktifkan fitur :guilabel:`Accept Terms & "
"Conditions`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:234
msgid ""
"Enable the :ref:`developer mode <developer-mode>` and click the :icon:`fa-"
"bug` (:guilabel:`bug`) icon to display an :ref:`availability "
"<payment_providers/availability>` report for payment providers and payment "
"methods, which helps diagnose potential availability issues on the payment "
"form."
msgstr ""
"Aktifkan :ref:`mode pengembang <developer-mode>` dan klik ikon :icon:`fa-"
"bug` (:guilabel:`bug`) untuk menampilkan laporan :ref:`ketersediaan "
"<payment_providers/availability>` untuk penyedia pembayaran dan metode "
"pembayaran, yang membantu mendiagnosis potensi masalah ketersediaan pada "
"formulir pembayaran."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:242
msgid "Order confirmation"
msgstr "Konfirmasi pesanan"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:244
msgid ""
"The final step of the checkout process is the :guilabel:`Order "
"confirmation`, which provides a summary of the customer's purchase details."
msgstr ""
"Langkah terakhir dari proses checkout adalah :guilabel:`Konfirmasi pesanan`, "
"yang menyediakan ringkasan detail pembelian pelanggan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:248
msgid ":doc:`Order handling documentation <order_handling>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Dokumentasi penanganan pesanan <order_handling>`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:3
#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:124
msgid "Customer accounts"
msgstr "Akun pelanggan"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:5
msgid ""
"Using customer accounts for an ecommerce shop enables you to :ref:`manage "
"customers <ecommerce/customer_accounts/account-creation>`, control access to "
"the :ref:`shop <ecommerce/customer_accounts/shop-access>`, "
"the :ref:`checkout <ecommerce/customer_accounts/checkout-access>`, or "
"the :ref:`customer portal <portal/access>`, and support both :doc:`B2B and "
"B2C operations <b2b_b2c>`."
msgstr ""
"Menggunakan akun pelanggan untuk toko ecommerce memungkinkan Anda untuk "
":ref:`mengelola pelanggan <ecommerce/customer_accounts/account-creation>`, "
"mengontrol akses ke :ref:`shop <ecommerce/customer_accounts/shop-access>`, "
":ref:`checkout <ecommerce/customer_accounts/checkout-access>`, atau "
":ref:`portal pelanggan <portal/access>`, dan mendukung :doc:`operasi B2B dan "
"B2C <b2b_b2c>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:11
msgid ""
"After logging in, customers can access their :doc:`customer portal <../../"
"general/users/portal>` by clicking their username in the top-right corner of "
"the screen and selecting :guilabel:`My Account`. From there, they can view "
"all their documents in one place, such as quotations, orders, invoices, and "
"more."
msgstr ""
"Setelah login, pelanggan dapat mengakses :doc:`portal pelanggan <../../"
"general/users/portal>` mereka dengan mengklik nama pengguna mereka di sudut "
"kanan atas layar dan memilih :guilabel:`My Account`. Dari sana, mereka dapat "
"melihat semua dokumen mereka di satu tempat, seperti penawaran, pesanan, "
"invoice, dan lainnya."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:None
msgid "Customer account access"
msgstr "Akses akun pelanggan"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:20
msgid ""
"The customer account page can be customized with building blocks and other "
"features through the :doc:`website builder <../website/web_design>`."
msgstr ""
"Halaman akun pelanggan dapat disesuaikan dengan building blocks dan fitur "
"lainnya melalui :doc:`website builder <../website/web_design>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:26
msgid "Customer account creation"
msgstr "Pembuatan akun pelanggan"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:28
msgid ""
"You can choose whether customer accounts and document access are available "
"to everyone or restricted to invited users only. To do so, go "
"to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings`, then scroll down "
"to the :guilabel:`Privacy` section. Under :guilabel:`Customer Account`, "
"select one of the following options:"
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat memilih apakah akun pelanggan dan akses dokumen tersedia untuk "
"semua orang atau dibatasi hanya untuk pengguna yang diundang. Untuk "
"melakukannya, buka :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings`, "
"lalu gulir ke bawah ke bagian :guilabel:`Privacy`. Di bawah "
":guilabel:`Customer Account`, pilih salah satu opsi berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:33
msgid ""
":guilabel:`On invitation`: Customers can only create an account if the "
"website owner sends them an invitation."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`On invitation`: Pelanggan hanya dapat membuat akun jika pemilik "
"website mengirimkan undangan kepada mereka."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:35
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Free sign up`: Every website visitor can create an account and "
"sign in. They will get access to the :doc:`portal <../../general/users/"
"portal>` by default."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Free sign up`: Setiap pengunjung website dapat membuat akun dan "
"login. Mereka akan mendapatkan akses ke :doc:`portal <../../general/users/"
"portal>` secara default."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:40
msgid "To send an email invitation to a customer:"
msgstr "Untuk mengirimkan undangan email ke pelanggan:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:42
msgid "Go to :menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce --> Customers`."
msgstr "Buka :menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce --> Customers`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:43
msgid ""
"Select a customer or click :guilabel:`New` to create one, ensuring "
"an :guilabel:`Email` address is set."
msgstr ""
"Pilih pelanggan atau klik :guilabel:`New` untuk membuat satu, pastikan "
"alamat :guilabel:`Email` telah diatur."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:45
msgid ""
"Click the :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`(Actions)` icon next to the record's "
"name at the top-left and select :guilabel:`Grant portal access`."
msgstr ""
"Klik ikon :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`(Actions)` di sebelah nama record di "
"kiri atas dan pilih :guilabel:`Grant portal access`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:47
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Portal Access Management` pop-up, click :guilabel:`Grant "
"Access` to send the invitation."
msgstr ""
"Dalam pop-up :guilabel:`Portal Access Management`, klik :guilabel:`Grant "
"Access` untuk mengirim undangan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:51
msgid ""
"To invite multiple customers at once, switch to the customers :icon:`oi-view-"
"list` :guilabel:`List` view, select several customers, click the :icon:`fa-"
"cog` :guilabel:`Actions` button, and select :guilabel:`Grant portal access`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengundang beberapa pelanggan sekaligus, beralih ke tampilan :icon:`oi-"
"view-list` :guilabel:`List` pelanggan, pilih beberapa pelanggan, klik tombol "
":icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`Actions`, dan pilih :guilabel:`Grant portal "
"access`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:55
msgid ""
"Once done, the customer(s) receive an email confirming their account "
"creation, including instructions on setting a password and activating their "
"account."
msgstr ""
"Setelah selesai, pelanggan akan menerima email yang mengonfirmasi pembuatan "
"akun mereka, termasuk instruksi untuk mengatur kata sandi dan mengaktifkan "
"akun mereka."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:59
msgid ""
"When selecting the :guilabel:`Free sign up`, a clickable :guilabel:`Don't "
"have an account?` link appears under the login form on the website."
msgstr ""
"Saat memilih :guilabel:`Free sign up`, tautan :guilabel:`Don't have an "
"account?` yang dapat diklik muncul di bawah formulir login di website."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:61
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`On invitation` option is especially useful for :ref:`B2B "
"<ecommerce/b2b_b2c/prices>` businesses that prefer to keep :ref:`prices "
"hidden <ecommerce/prices/hide-prices>` on the website and grant access only "
"to invited customers."
msgstr ""
"Opsi :guilabel:`On invitation` sangat berguna untuk bisnis :ref:`B2B "
"<ecommerce/b2b_b2c/prices>` yang lebih suka :ref:`menyembunyikan harga "
"<ecommerce/prices/hide-prices>` di website dan hanya memberikan akses kepada "
"pelanggan yang diundang."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:66
msgid ""
"It is possible to configure a website form with a :guilabel:`Create a "
"Customer` :ref:`action <website/building_blocks/action>` to automatically "
"create a customer record in the backend when filled in."
msgstr ""
"Dimungkinkan untuk mengonfigurasi formulir website dengan :guilabel:`Create "
"a Customer` :ref:`action <website/building_blocks/action>` untuk secara "
"otomatis membuat catatan pelanggan di backend saat diisi."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:71
msgid "Access restriction"
msgstr "Batasan akses"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:73
msgid ""
"Once a customer account is created, it is still possible to adjust the "
"access rights either globally or for individual users:"
msgstr ""
"Setelah akun pelanggan dibuat, masih dimungkinkan untuk menyesuaikan hak "
"akses baik secara global maupun untuk pengguna individual:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:76
msgid ""
":ref:`Revoke access or re-invite a customer <portal/access>` using the "
"related buttons in the :guilabel:`Portal Access Management` pop-up."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Cabut akses atau undang kembali pelanggan <portal/access>` menggunakan "
"tombol terkait di pop-up :guilabel:`Portal Access Management`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:78
msgid ""
"Restrict :ref:`access to the shop <ecommerce/customer_accounts/shop-access>`;"
msgstr "Batasi :ref:`akses ke toko <ecommerce/customer_accounts/shop-access>`;"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:79
msgid ""
"Decide whether customers need to create an account to :ref:`complete the "
"checkout <ecommerce/customer_accounts/checkout-access>`."
msgstr ""
"Tentukan apakah pelanggan perlu membuat akun untuk :ref:`menyelesaikan "
"checkout <ecommerce/customer_accounts/checkout-access>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:83
msgid ""
"It is also possible to define the types of documents customers have access "
"to. To do so, click your username in the upper-right corner of the website, "
"select :guilabel:`My Account` and open the :doc:`website builder <../website/"
"web_design>`. On the :guilabel:`Customize` tab, enable or disable access to "
"specific documents as needed."
msgstr ""
"Dimungkinkan juga untuk menentukan jenis dokumen yang dapat diakses "
"pelanggan. Untuk melakukannya, klik nama pengguna Anda di sudut kanan atas "
"website, pilih :guilabel:`My Account` dan buka :doc:`website builder <../"
"website/web_design>`. Pada tab :guilabel:`Customize`, aktifkan atau "
"nonaktifkan akses ke dokumen tertentu sesuai kebutuhan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:91
msgid "Shop access"
msgstr "Akses toko"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:93
msgid ""
"To restrict access to the entire online shop for users who are not logged-"
"in, go to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings`, scroll "
"to :guilabel:`Privacy` and under :guilabel:`Ecommerce Access`, "
"select :guilabel:`Logged in users`. Select :guilabel:`All users` if the shop "
"should be visible to every website visitor."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membatasi akses ke seluruh toko online untuk pengguna yang tidak "
"login, buka :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings`, gulir "
"ke :guilabel:`Privacy` dan di bawah :guilabel:`Ecommerce Access`, pilih "
":guilabel:`Logged in users`. Pilih :guilabel:`All users` jika toko harus "
"terlihat oleh setiap pengunjung website."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:99
msgid ""
"To restrict access to the shop's pricing, use :ref:`pricelists <ecommerce/"
"prices/pricelists>` with :ref:`country groups <ecommerce/prices/country-"
"groups>`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membatasi akses ke harga toko, gunakan :ref:`pricelist <ecommerce/"
"prices/pricelists>` dengan :ref:`grup negara <ecommerce/prices/country-"
"groups>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:105
msgid "Checkout access"
msgstr "Akses checkout"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:107
msgid ""
"To allow customers to checkout as guests or force them to sign in/create an "
"account, go to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings`, "
"scroll down to the :guilabel:`Shop - Checkout Process` section, and "
"configure the :guilabel:`Sign in/up at checkout` setting. The following "
"options are available:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengizinkan pelanggan checkout sebagai tamu atau memaksa mereka untuk "
"sign in/membuat akun, buka :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> "
"Settings`, gulir ke bawah ke bagian :guilabel:`Shop - Checkout Process`, dan "
"konfigurasikan pengaturan :guilabel:`Sign in/up at checkout`. Opsi berikut "
"tersedia:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:112
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Optional`: Customers can check out as guests and register later "
"via the order confirmation email to track their order."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Opsional`: Pelanggan dapat checkout sebagai tamu dan mendaftar "
"nanti melalui email konfirmasi pesanan untuk melacak pesanan mereka."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:114
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Disabled (buy as guest)`: Customers can checkout as guests "
"without creating an account."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Disabled (buy as guest)`: Pelanggan dapat checkout sebagai tamu "
"tanpa membuat akun."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:115
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Mandatory (no guest checkout)`: Customers must sign in or create "
"an account at the :ref:`Review Order <ecommerce/checkout/review_order>` step "
"to complete their purchase."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Mandatory (no guest checkout)`: Pelanggan harus sign in atau "
"membuat akun pada tahap :ref:`Review Order <ecommerce/checkout/review_order>"
"` untuk menyelesaikan pembelian mereka."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:119
msgid ""
"Settings are specific to each website, allowing you to configure a B2C "
"website with guest checkout and a B2B website that requires customers to "
"sign in."
msgstr ""
"Pengaturan bersifat khusus untuk setiap website, memungkinkan Anda "
"mengonfigurasi website B2C dengan checkout tamu dan website B2B yang "
"mengharuskan pelanggan untuk login."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:121
msgid ""
"To use the :ref:`wishlist <ecommerce/products/wishlists>` feature, customers "
"must create an account to save their favorite items for later."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menggunakan fitur :ref:`wishlist <ecommerce/products/wishlists>`, "
"pelanggan harus membuat akun untuk menyimpan item favorit mereka untuk nanti."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:127
msgid "Multi-website account"
msgstr "Akun multi-website"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:129
msgid ""
"When managing multiple websites, it is possible to make customer accounts "
"available across *all* websites, allowing each customer to use a single "
"account. To do so, go to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> "
"Settings`, in the :guilabel:`Privacy` section, enable the :guilabel:`Shared "
"Customer Accounts` option."
msgstr ""
"Saat mengelola beberapa website, dimungkinkan untuk membuat akun pelanggan "
"tersedia di *semua* website, memungkinkan setiap pelanggan menggunakan satu "
"akun. Untuk melakukannya, buka :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> "
"Settings`, di bagian :guilabel:`Privacy`, aktifkan opsi :guilabel:`Shared "
"Customer Accounts`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:135
msgid ""
"When operating both :ref:`B2B and B2C online shops <ecommerce/b2b_b2c/"
"multiple-websites>`, it is recommended to use separate websites for each "
"business model."
msgstr ""
"Saat mengoperasikan :ref:`toko online B2B dan B2C <ecommerce/b2b_b2c/"
"multiple-websites>`, disarankan untuk menggunakan website terpisah untuk "
"setiap model bisnis."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:3
msgid "Order handling"
msgstr "Penanganan pesanan"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:5
msgid ""
"When a customer orders on your eCommerce, there are **three** record types "
"required to be handle in Odoo:"
msgstr ""
"Ketika pelanggan memesan di eCommerce Anda, ada **tiga** jenis catatan yang "
"perlu ditangani di Odoo:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:8
msgid ":ref:`Sales orders <handling/sales>`;"
msgstr ":ref:`Sales order <handling/sales>`;"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:9
msgid ":ref:`Delivery orders <handling/delivery>`;"
msgstr ":ref:`Pesanan pengiriman <handling/delivery>`;"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:10
msgid ":ref:`Invoices & legal requirements <handling/legal>`."
msgstr ":ref:`Faktur & persyaratan hukum <handling/legal>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:15
msgid "Sales orders"
msgstr "Sale order"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:18
msgid "Order and payment status"
msgstr "Status pesanan dan pembayaran"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:20
msgid ""
"The first step when a customer adds a product to his cart is the creation of "
"a quotation. Orders can be managed either from the **Website** "
"or :doc:`Sales </applications/sales/sales>` app. eCommerce orders can "
"automatically be assigned to a specific sales team by going "
"to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings`. In the **Shop - "
"Checkout Process** section, select a :guilabel:`Sales Team` "
"or :guilabel:`Salesperson` to handle eCommerce orders."
msgstr ""
"Langkah pertama ketika pelanggan menambahkan produk ke keranjang adalah "
"pembuatan penawaran. Pesanan dapat dikelola dari aplikasi **Website** atau "
":doc:`Sales </applications/sales/sales>`. Pesanan eCommerce dapat secara "
"otomatis ditetapkan ke tim penjualan tertentu dengan membuka "
":menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings`. Di bagian **Shop - "
"Checkout Process**, pilih :guilabel:`Sales Team` atau "
":guilabel:`Salesperson` untuk menangani pesanan eCommerce."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:None
msgid "Assignment of online orders to a sales team or salesperson"
msgstr "Penugasan pesanan online ke tim penjualan atau salesperson"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:30
msgid ""
"Orders can be found under :menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce --> Orders/"
"Unpaid Orders`. Each order goes through a different status:"
msgstr ""
"Pesanan dapat ditemukan di bawah :menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce --> "
"Orders/Unpaid Orders`. Setiap pesanan melalui status yang berbeda:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:33
msgid ""
"**Quotation**: a new product is added to the cart, but the customer has "
"*not* gone through the checkout process yet;"
msgstr ""
"**Quotation**: produk baru ditambahkan ke keranjang, tetapi pelanggan "
"*belum* melalui proses checkout;"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:35
msgid ""
"**Quotation sent**: the customer has gone through the checkout process and "
"confirmed the order, but the payment is not yet confirmed;"
msgstr ""
"**Quotation sent**: pelanggan telah melalui proses checkout dan "
"mengonfirmasi pesanan, tetapi pembayaran belum dikonfirmasi;"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:37
msgid ""
"**Order**: the customer has gone through the checkout process, confirmed the "
"order, and the payment is received."
msgstr ""
"**Order**: pelanggan telah melalui proses checkout, mengonfirmasi pesanan, "
"dan pembayaran telah diterima."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:None
msgid "Statuses of eCommerce orders"
msgstr "Status pesanan eCommerce"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:45
msgid "Abandoned cart"
msgstr "Keranjang yang ditinggalkan"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:47
msgid ""
"An **abandoned cart** represents an order for which the customer did **not "
"finish** the checkout confirmation process. For these orders, it is possible "
"to send an **email reminder** to the customer automatically. To enable that "
"feature, go to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings` and "
"in the :guilabel:`Email & Marketing` section, "
"enable :guilabel:`Automatically send abandoned checkout emails`. Once "
"enabled, you can set the **time-lapse** after which the email is sent and "
"customize the **email template** used."
msgstr ""
"**Keranjang yang ditinggalkan** mewakili pesanan di mana pelanggan **tidak "
"menyelesaikan** proses konfirmasi checkout. Untuk pesanan ini, dimungkinkan "
"untuk mengirim **pengingat email** kepada pelanggan secara otomatis. Untuk "
"mengaktifkan fitur tersebut, buka :menuselection:`Website --> "
"Configuration --> Settings` dan di bagian :guilabel:`Email & Marketing`, "
"aktifkan :guilabel:`Automatically send abandoned checkout emails`. Setelah "
"diaktifkan, Anda dapat mengatur **jangka waktu** setelah email dikirim dan "
"menyesuaikan **template email** yang digunakan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:55
msgid ""
"For abandoned cart emails, the customer must either have entered their "
"contact details during the checkout process; or be logged-in when they added "
"the product to their cart."
msgstr ""
"Untuk email keranjang yang ditinggalkan, pelanggan harus memasukkan detail "
"kontak mereka selama proses checkout; atau masuk saat mereka menambahkan "
"produk ke keranjang mereka."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:61
msgid "Delivery orders"
msgstr "Surat jalan"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:64
msgid "Delivery flow"
msgstr "Alur pengiriman"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:66
msgid ""
"Once a quotation has been confirmed, a delivery order is automatically "
"created. The next step is to process this delivery."
msgstr ""
"Setelah quotation dikonfirmasi, surat jalan dibuat secara otomatis. Langkah "
"selanjutnya adalah memproses pengiriman ini."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:69
msgid ""
"Packing eCommerce orders usually requires picking the product, preparing the "
"packaging, printing the shipping label(s) and shipping to the customer. "
"Depending on the number of orders, strategy, or resources, those steps can "
"be considered as one or multiple actions in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Packing pesanan eCommerce biasanya memerlukan picking produk, menyiapkan "
"kemasan, mencetak label pengiriman dan mengirim ke pelanggan. Tergantung "
"pada jumlah pesanan, strategi, atau sumber daya, langkah-langkah tersebut "
"dapat dianggap sebagai satu atau beberapa tindakan di Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:73
msgid ""
"An automatic email can be sent to the customer when the transfer status in "
"Odoo is “done”. To do so, enable the feature in the settings of "
"the :doc:`Inventory </applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory>` app."
msgstr ""
"Email otomatis dapat dikirim ke pelanggan ketika status transfer di Odoo "
"adalah \"done\". Untuk melakukannya, aktifkan fitur di pengaturan aplikasi "
":doc:`Inventaris </applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:78
msgid ""
"If customers are allowed to pay when picking up their order in stores or by "
"wire transfer, the quotation is **not** be confirmed and the stock is "
"**not** be reserved. Orders must be confirmed manually to reserve products "
"in stock."
msgstr ""
"Jika pelanggan diizinkan untuk membayar saat mengambil pesanan mereka di "
"toko atau melalui transfer bank, quotation **tidak** dikonfirmasi dan stok "
"**tidak** dipesan. Pesanan harus dikonfirmasi secara manual untuk memesan "
"produk dalam stok."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:83
msgid ""
":doc:`../../inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"setup_configuration/invoicing`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`../../inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"setup_configuration/invoicing`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:84
msgid ""
":doc:`../../inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"setup_configuration/labels`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`../../inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"setup_configuration/labels`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:85
msgid ""
":doc:`../../inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"setup_configuration/multipack`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`../../inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"setup_configuration/multipack`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:88
msgid "Returns and refunds"
msgstr "Pengembalian dan pengembalian dana"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:90
msgid ""
"Customers can only return an order through an online form. It may not be "
"possible to return products depending on the return strategy or type of "
"product."
msgstr ""
"Pelanggan hanya dapat mengembalikan pesanan melalui formulir online. Mungkin "
"tidak dapat mengembalikan produk tergantung pada strategi pengembalian atau "
"jenis produk."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:93
msgid ""
"Full refunds can be directly sent to customers from within the order "
"interface. A refund-compatible payment provider needs to be enabled first."
msgstr ""
"Pengembalian dana penuh dapat langsung dikirim ke pelanggan dari dalam "
"antarmuka pesanan. Penyedia pembayaran yang kompatibel dengan pengembalian "
"dana perlu diaktifkan terlebih dahulu."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:97
msgid ":doc:`/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns`"
msgstr ":doc:`/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:98
msgid ":doc:`/applications/services/helpdesk/advanced/after_sales`"
msgstr ":doc:`/applications/services/helpdesk/advanced/after_sales`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:99
msgid ":doc:`/applications/finance/payment_providers`"
msgstr ":doc:`/applications/finance/payment_providers`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:104
msgid "Invoice and legal requirements"
msgstr "Persyaratan faktur dan hukum"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:106
msgid ""
"The final step of an ecommerce order is to generate the invoice and send it "
"to the customer. Depending on your needs, an invoice can either be generated "
"automatically or on demand of the customer. This process can be automated if "
"(and when) the online payment is :ref:`confirmed <handling/sales>`."
msgstr ""
"Langkah terakhir dari pesanan ecommerce adalah membuat invoice dan "
"mengirimkannya ke pelanggan. Tergantung kebutuhan Anda, invoice dapat dibuat "
"secara otomatis atau atas permintaan pelanggan. Proses ini dapat "
"diotomatisasi jika (dan ketika) pembayaran online :ref:`dikonfirmasi "
"<handling/sales>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:111
msgid ""
"To automate invoicing, go to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> "
"Settings` and in the :guilabel:`Invoicing` section, "
"enable :guilabel:`Automatic Invoice`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengotomatiskan penagihan, buka :menuselection:`Website --> "
"Configuration --> Settings` dan di bagian :guilabel:`Invoicing`, aktifkan "
":guilabel:`Automatic Invoice`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/payments.rst:3
msgid "Payment providers"
msgstr "Penyedia pembayaran"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/payments.rst:5
msgid ""
"Odoo supports a multitude of online :doc:`payment providers </applications/"
"finance/payment_providers>` for your website, allowing your customers to pay "
"with their preferred payment methods."
msgstr ""
"Odoo mendukung berbagai :doc:`penyedia pembayaran </applications/finance/"
"payment_providers>` online untuk website Anda, memungkinkan pelanggan Anda "
"membayar dengan metode pembayaran pilihan mereka."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/payments.rst:10
#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/payments.rst:54
msgid ":doc:`/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards`"
msgstr ":doc:`/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/payments.rst:11
msgid ":doc:`checkout`"
msgstr ":doc:`checkout`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/payments.rst:14
#: ../../content/applications/websites/website.rst:28
#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration.rst:5
#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:21
#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/reporting/link_tracker.rst:10
msgid "Configuration"
msgstr "Konfigurasi"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/payments.rst:16
msgid ""
"To set up payment providers on the eCommerce app, go "
"to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Payment Providers`. From "
"here, :guilabel:`Activate` the payment providers you wish to have available "
"on your shop, and configure them according to your needs."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengatur penyedia pembayaran pada aplikasi eCommerce, buka "
":menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Payment Providers`. Dari sini, "
":guilabel:`Activate` penyedia pembayaran yang ingin Anda sediakan di toko "
"Anda, dan konfigurasikan sesuai kebutuhan Anda."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/payments.rst:20
msgid ""
"Alternatively, you can access **payment providers** "
"via :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings`. In "
"the :guilabel:`Shop - Payment` section, you can :guilabel:`Configure SEPA "
"Direct Debit` if you wish to use it, as well as :guilabel:`View other "
"providers`. If you use the :guilabel:`Authorize.net` payment provider, "
"the :ref:`Payment Capture Method <payment_providers/manual_capture>` can be "
"configured in that same menu."
msgstr ""
"Atau, Anda dapat mengakses **penyedia pembayaran** melalui "
":menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings`. Di bagian "
":guilabel:`Shop - Payment`, Anda dapat :guilabel:`Configure SEPA Direct "
"Debit` jika ingin menggunakannya, serta :guilabel:`View other providers`. "
"Jika Anda menggunakan penyedia pembayaran :guilabel:`Authorize.net`, "
":ref:`Metode Penangkapan Pembayaran <payment_providers/manual_capture>` "
"dapat dikonfigurasi di menu yang sama."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/payments.rst:26
msgid ""
"If you are using :doc:`/applications/finance/payment_providers/paypal`, you "
"can also enable and configure it here."
msgstr ""
"Jika Anda menggunakan :doc:`/applications/finance/payment_providers/paypal`, "
"Anda juga dapat mengaktifkan dan mengonfigurasinya di sini."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/payments.rst:30
msgid "Checkout payment options"
msgstr "Opsi pembayaran checkout"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/payments.rst:32
msgid ""
"Once activated, customers can choose the payment provider of their choice "
"during the **checkout process**, at the :guilabel:`Confirm Order` step."
msgstr ""
"Setelah diaktifkan, pelanggan dapat memilih penyedia pembayaran pilihan "
"mereka selama **proses checkout**, pada langkah :guilabel:`Confirm Order`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/payments.rst:None
msgid "Payment provider selection at checkout"
msgstr "Pemilihan penyedia pembayaran saat checkout"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/payments.rst:40
msgid "eWallets and gift cards"
msgstr "Dompet elektronik dan kartu hadiah"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/payments.rst:42
msgid ""
"When checking out, customers can pay with an eWallet or gift cards. To "
"enable these, go to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings`, "
"and in the :guilabel:`Shop-Products` section, "
"enable :menuselection:`Discounts, Loyalty & Gift Card`."
msgstr ""
"Saat checkout, pelanggan dapat membayar dengan eWallet atau kartu hadiah. "
"Untuk mengaktifkannya, buka :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> "
"Settings`, dan di bagian :guilabel:`Shop-Products`, aktifkan "
":menuselection:`Discounts, Loyalty & Gift Card`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/payments.rst:46
msgid ""
"Once enabled, customers can enter their gift card **code** or pay with their "
"eWallet at the checkout step."
msgstr ""
"Setelah diaktifkan, pelanggan dapat memasukkan **kode** kartu hadiah mereka "
"atau membayar dengan eWallet mereka pada langkah checkout."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/payments.rst:None
msgid "Enter gift card code to process checkout"
msgstr "Masukkan kode kartu hadiah untuk memproses checkout"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:3
msgid "Performance management"
msgstr "Manajemen performa"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:5
msgid ""
"Odoo integrates a variety of tools to analyze and improve the performance of "
"your eCommerce website."
msgstr ""
"Odoo mengintegrasikan berbagai alat untuk menganalisis dan meningkatkan "
"kinerja website eCommerce Anda."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:9
msgid "Data monitoring"
msgstr "Pemantauan data"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:11
msgid ""
"**Website** allows monitoring and analysis of the sales performance of your "
"eCommerce. To access the **reporting view**, go to :menuselection:`Website --"
"> Reporting --> eCommerce`. This dashboard helps you monitor everything "
"related to sales, such as sales performance per product, category, day, etc."
msgstr ""
"**Website** memungkinkan pemantauan dan analisis kinerja penjualan eCommerce "
"Anda. Untuk mengakses **tampilan pelaporan**, buka "
":menuselection:`Website --> Reporting --> eCommerce`. Dashboard ini membantu "
"Anda memantau semua hal terkait penjualan, seperti kinerja penjualan per "
"produk, kategori, hari, dll."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:None
msgid "Performance reporting of eCommerce"
msgstr "Pelaporan kinerja eCommerce"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:19
msgid ""
"By clicking :guilabel:`Measures`, you can select the type of measurement "
"used, such as:"
msgstr ""
"Dengan mengklik :guilabel:`Measures`, Anda dapat memilih jenis pengukuran "
"yang digunakan, seperti:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:21
msgid ":guilabel:`Margin`;"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Margin`;"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:22
msgid ":guilabel:`Qty Invoiced`;"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Qty Invoiced`;"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:23
msgid ":guilabel:`Untaxed Total`;"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Untaxed Total`;"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:24
msgid ":guilabel:`Volume`;"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Volume`;"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:25
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:27
msgid ""
"Other options include **multiple views (Pivot, etc.), comparison** by "
"periods or years, and directly :guilabel:`insert in spreadsheet`, etc."
msgstr ""
"Opsi lainnya mencakup **beberapa tampilan (Pivot, dll.), perbandingan** "
"berdasarkan periode atau tahun, dan langsung :guilabel:`masukkan dalam "
"spreadsheet`, dll."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:31
#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:147
msgid "Analytics"
msgstr "Analitik"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:33
msgid ""
"It is possible to link your Odoo website with :ref:`analytics/plausible` "
"and :ref:`analytics/google-analytics`."
msgstr ""
"Dimungkinkan untuk menghubungkan website Odoo Anda dengan :ref:`analytics/"
"plausible` dan :ref:`analytics/google-analytics`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:39
msgid "Email queue optimization"
msgstr "Optimasi antrian email"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:41
msgid ""
"For websites handling flash sales (e.g., event ticket sales) or experiencing "
"high traffic spikes, order confirmation emails can become a performance "
"bottleneck, potentially slowing down the checkout process for other "
"customers."
msgstr ""
"Untuk website yang menangani flash sale (misalnya penjualan tiket acara) "
"atau mengalami lonjakan lalu lintas tinggi, email konfirmasi pesanan dapat "
"menjadi hambatan performa, yang berpotensi memperlambat proses checkout bagi "
"pelanggan lain."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:45
msgid ""
"To improve performance, these emails can be queued and processed separately "
"from the order confirmation flow. This is managed by the :guilabel:`Sales: "
"Send pending emails` scheduled action, which sends queued emails as soon as "
"possible."
msgstr ""
"Untuk meningkatkan performa, email ini dapat diantrekan dan diproses secara "
"terpisah dari alur konfirmasi pesanan. Hal ini dikelola oleh tindakan "
"terjadwal :guilabel:`Sales: Send pending emails`, yang mengirim email yang "
"diantrekan sesegera mungkin."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:49
msgid "To enable asynchronous email sending:"
msgstr "Untuk mengaktifkan pengiriman email asinkron:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:51
msgid ""
"Enable the :doc:`developer mode </applications/general/developer_mode>`."
msgstr "Aktifkan :doc:`mode pengembang </applications/general/developer_mode>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:52
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Apps`, remove the :guilabel:`Apps` filter, and install "
"the :guilabel:`Sales - Async Emails` module."
msgstr ""
"Buka :menuselection:`Apps`, hapus filter :guilabel:`Apps`, dan instal modul "
":guilabel:`Sales - Async Emails`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:54
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Settings --> Technical --> System Parameters` and set "
"the :guilabel:`sale.async_emails` system parameter to `True`."
msgstr ""
"Buka :menuselection:`Settings --> Technical --> System Parameters` dan atur "
"parameter sistem :guilabel:`sale.async_emails` menjadi `True`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:56
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Settings --> Technical --> Scheduled Actions` and "
"ensure that the :guilabel:`Sales: Send pending emails` scheduled action is "
"enabled."
msgstr ""
"Buka :menuselection:`Settings --> Technical --> Scheduled Actions` dan "
"pastikan tindakan terjadwal :guilabel:`Sales: Send pending emails` "
"diaktifkan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:60
msgid ""
"Enabling this feature may delay order confirmation and invoice emails by a "
"few minutes. It is recommended only for high-traffic websites, as it can "
"introduce unnecessary delays for e-commerce websites with moderate traffic."
msgstr ""
"Mengaktifkan fitur ini dapat menunda email konfirmasi pesanan dan faktur "
"selama beberapa menit. Fitur ini hanya disarankan untuk website dengan lalu "
"lintas tinggi, karena dapat menimbulkan penundaan yang tidak perlu untuk "
"website eCommerce dengan lalu lintas sedang."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:5
msgid "Products"
msgstr "Produk"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:7
msgid ""
"**Odoo eCommerce** allows you to :ref:`add products <ecommerce/products/add-"
"products>` and manage your :ref:`product pages <ecommerce/products/product-"
"page>` directly from the Website app. It also allows you to "
"add :ref:`product variants <ecommerce/products/product-variants>` "
"and :ref:`digital files <ecommerce/products/digital-"
"files>`, :ref:`translating <ecommerce/products/translation>` the product "
"page content, :ref:`managing stock <ecommerce/products/stock-management>`, "
"and enabling :ref:`product comparisons <ecommerce/products/product-"
"comparison>`."
msgstr ""
"**Odoo eCommerce** memungkinkan Anda untuk :ref:`menambahkan produk "
"<ecommerce/products/add-products>` dan mengelola :ref:`halaman produk "
"<ecommerce/products/product-page>` Anda langsung dari aplikasi Website. "
"Fitur ini juga memungkinkan Anda untuk menambahkan :ref:`varian produk "
"<ecommerce/products/product-variants>` dan :ref:`file digital <ecommerce/"
"products/digital-files>`, :ref:`menerjemahkan <ecommerce/products/"
"translation>` konten halaman produk, :ref:`mengelola stok <ecommerce/"
"products/stock-management>`, dan mengaktifkan :ref:`perbandingan produk "
"<ecommerce/products/product-comparison>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:18
msgid "Add products"
msgstr "Tambahkan produk-produk"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:23
msgid "Create products"
msgstr "Buat produk"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:25
msgid ""
"To create a product from the frontend, click :guilabel:`+ New` in the top-"
"right corner, then :guilabel:`Product`. Enter the :guilabel:`Product "
"Name`, :guilabel:`Sales Price`, the default :guilabel:`Customer Taxes` for "
"local transactions, and :guilabel:`Save`. You can then update the product's "
"details, add an image, and :ref:`customize <ecommerce/products/"
"customization>` the product page. When you :guilabel:`Save`, the product "
"page is automatically published."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat produk dari frontend, klik :guilabel:`+ New` di sudut kanan "
"atas, kemudian :guilabel:`Product`. Masukkan :guilabel:`Product Name`, "
":guilabel:`Sales Price`, :guilabel:`Customer Taxes` default untuk transaksi "
"lokal, dan :guilabel:`Save`. Anda kemudian dapat memperbarui detail produk, "
"menambahkan gambar, dan :ref:`menyesuaikan <ecommerce/products/customization>"
"` halaman produk. Ketika Anda :guilabel:`Save`, halaman produk akan otomatis "
"dipublikasikan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:32
msgid ""
"You can also create a product from the backend by going "
"to :menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce --> Products` and "
"clicking :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr ""
"Anda juga dapat membuat produk dari backend dengan membuka "
":menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce --> Products` dan mengklik "
":guilabel:`New`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:34
msgid ""
"Products created from the frontend are automatically :ref:`published "
"<website/pages/un-publish-page>`, while products created from the backend "
"are not. To publish a product, click the :guilabel:`Go to Website` smart "
"button to access the product page, then toggle the switch "
"from :guilabel:`Unpublished` to :guilabel:`Published`."
msgstr ""
"Produk yang dibuat dari frontend secara otomatis :ref:`dipublikasikan "
"<website/pages/un-publish-page>`, sedangkan produk yang dibuat dari backend "
"tidak. Untuk mempublikasikan produk, klik tombol pintar :guilabel:`Go to "
"Website` untuk mengakses halaman produk, kemudian alihkan sakelar dari "
":guilabel:`Unpublished` ke :guilabel:`Published`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:40
msgid ""
":doc:`Create new products using the Barcode Lookup database </applications/"
"inventory_and_mrp/barcode/setup/barcodelookup>`."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Buat produk baru menggunakan database Barcode Lookup </applications/"
"inventory_and_mrp/barcode/setup/barcodelookup>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:46
msgid "Import products"
msgstr "Impor produk"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:48
msgid ""
"To :ref:`import product data <essentials/export_import_data/import-data>` "
"using XLSX or CSV files, go to :menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce --> "
"Products`, click the :icon:`fa-cog` (:guilabel:`gear`) icon, "
"then :ref:`Import records <essentials/export_import_data/import-data>`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk :ref:`mengimpor data produk <essentials/export_import_data/import-data>"
"` menggunakan file XLSX atau CSV, buka :menuselection:`Website --> "
"eCommerce --> Products`, klik ikon :icon:`fa-cog` (:guilabel:`gear`), "
"kemudian :ref:`Import records <essentials/export_import_data/import-data>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:53
msgid "To publish **large batches** of products, follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk mempublikasikan **batch besar** produk, ikuti langkah-langkah berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:55
msgid "Go to :menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce --> Products`."
msgstr "Buka :menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce --> Products`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:56
msgid ""
"Remove the :guilabel:`Published` filter and switch to the :guilabel:`List` "
"view."
msgstr ""
"Hapus filter :guilabel:`Published` dan beralih ke tampilan :guilabel:`List`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:57
msgid ""
"Click the :icon:`fa-sliders` (:guilabel:`dropdown toggle`) icon and "
"enable :guilabel:`Is published`."
msgstr ""
"Klik ikon :icon:`fa-sliders` (:guilabel:`dropdown toggle`) dan aktifkan "
":guilabel:`Is published`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:59
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`Is Published` column to re-order it by **published** or "
"**unpublished** products."
msgstr ""
"Klik kolom :guilabel:`Is Published` untuk mengurutkannya berdasarkan produk "
"yang **dipublikasikan** atau **tidak dipublikasikan**."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:61
msgid "Select the products to publish by ticking their box."
msgstr "Pilih produk yang akan dipublikasikan dengan mencentang kotaknya."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:62
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Is Published` column, tick the box for any of the selected "
"products, then :guilabel:`Confirm` to publish them."
msgstr ""
"Di kolom :guilabel:`Is Published`, centang kotak untuk salah satu produk "
"yang dipilih, kemudian :guilabel:`Confirm` untuk mempublikasikannya."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:68
msgid "Product page customization"
msgstr "Kustomisasi halaman produk"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:73
msgid "Product information"
msgstr "Informasi produk"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:76
msgid ""
"To add general information about a product, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce --> Products` and select the "
"product. You can configure the product page from the form by "
"adding :ref:`variants <ecommerce/products/product-variants>`, :ref:`digital "
"documents <ecommerce/products/digital-files>`, or :ref:`translating "
"<ecommerce/products/translation>` content."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menambahkan informasi umum tentang produk, navigasi ke "
":menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce --> Products` dan pilih produk. Anda "
"dapat mengonfigurasi halaman produk dari formulir dengan menambahkan "
":ref:`varian <ecommerce/products/product-variants>`, :ref:`dokumen digital "
"<ecommerce/products/digital-files>`, atau :ref:`menerjemahkan <ecommerce/"
"products/translation>` konten."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:81
msgid ""
"You can also add an ecommerce-specific product description to be displayed "
"below the product name on the product's page. To do so, go to "
"the :guilabel:`Sales` tab, scroll down to the :guilabel:`Ecommerce "
"description` section, and add a description. Use Odoo's :doc:`rich-text "
"editor <../../essentials/html_editor>` features to personalize the content."
msgstr ""
"Anda juga dapat menambahkan deskripsi produk khusus eCommerce yang akan "
"ditampilkan di bawah nama produk pada halaman produk. Untuk melakukannya, "
"buka tab :guilabel:`Sales`, gulir ke bawah ke bagian :guilabel:`Deskripsi "
"Ecommerce`, dan tambahkan deskripsi. Gunakan fitur :doc:`editor rich-text "
"<../../essentials/html_editor>` Odoo untuk mempersonalisasi konten."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:87
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`Go to Website` smart button to return to the frontend "
"product's page."
msgstr ""
"Klik tombol pintar :guilabel:`Buka ke Website` untuk kembali ke halaman "
"produk frontend."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:92
msgid "Product presentation"
msgstr "Presentasi produk"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:94
msgid ""
"To customize the product presentation on the website, go to "
"the :guilabel:`Shop` and click on the product. Click :guilabel:`Edit` "
"to :ref:`customize <ecommerce/products/customization>` the page, :ref:`edit "
"its images <ecommerce/products/image-customization>` or add :doc:`building "
"blocks <../../websites/website/web_design/building_blocks>`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menyesuaikan presentasi produk di website, buka :guilabel:`Shop` dan "
"klik pada produk. Klik :guilabel:`Edit` untuk :ref:`menyesuaikan <ecommerce/"
"products/customization>` halaman, :ref:`mengedit gambarnya <ecommerce/"
"products/image-customization>` atau menambahkan :doc:`blok bangunan <../../"
"websites/website/web_design/building_blocks>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:100
msgid ""
"When dragging and dropping a building block on the product page, placing it "
"above or below the top or bottom blue lines makes it visible on all product "
"pages."
msgstr ""
"Saat menyeret dan melepas blok bangunan pada halaman produk, menempatkannya "
"di atas atau di bawah garis biru atas atau bawah membuatnya terlihat di "
"semua halaman produk."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:102
msgid ""
"You can edit any text on your website by clicking on it while "
"in :guilabel:`Edit` mode."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat mengedit teks apa pun di website Anda dengan mengkliknya saat "
"dalam mode :guilabel:`Edit`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:104
msgid ""
"Use the :guilabel:`Customize` tab to modify the page layout or add features:"
msgstr ""
"Gunakan tab :guilabel:`Customize` untuk memodifikasi tata letak halaman atau "
"menambahkan fitur:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:106
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Terms and Conditions`: Toggle the switch to display a link to "
"your :doc:`terms and conditions <../../finance/accounting/customer_invoices/"
"terms_conditions>` on the product page."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Syarat dan Ketentuan`: Aktifkan tombol untuk menampilkan tautan "
"ke :doc:`syarat dan ketentuan <../../finance/accounting/customer_invoices/"
"terms_conditions>` Anda pada halaman produk."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:110
msgid ":guilabel:`Customers`:"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Pelanggan`:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:112
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Rating`: Allow logged-in portal users to submit product reviews "
"by clicking the stars below the product's name and sharing their experience "
"in the :guilabel:`Customer Reviews` section at the bottom. Reviews are "
"visible from the product page using the :icon:`fa-plus` (:guilabel:`plus`) "
"icon next to the :guilabel:`Customer Reviews` heading or from the product "
"form's chatter. To restrict visibility to internal employees, toggle "
"the :guilabel:`Public` switch next to the review comment."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Penilaian`: Izinkan pengguna portal yang masuk untuk mengirimkan "
"ulasan produk dengan mengklik bintang di bawah nama produk dan membagikan "
"pengalaman mereka di bagian :guilabel:`Ulasan Pelanggan` di bagian bawah. "
"Ulasan terlihat dari halaman produk menggunakan ikon :icon:`fa-plus` "
"(:guilabel:`plus`) di samping judul :guilabel:`Ulasan Pelanggan` atau dari "
"chatter formulir produk. Untuk membatasi visibilitas ke karyawan internal "
"saja, aktifkan tombol :guilabel:`Publik` di samping komentar ulasan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:118
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Share`: Add social media and email icon buttons allowing "
"customers to share the product through those channels."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Bagikan`: Tambahkan tombol ikon media sosial dan email yang "
"memungkinkan pelanggan membagikan produk melalui saluran tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:121
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Select Quantity`: Toggle the switch to allow customers to select "
"the product quantity they want to purchase."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Pilih Kuantitas`: Aktifkan tombol untuk memungkinkan pelanggan "
"memilih jumlah produk yang ingin mereka beli."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:124
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Tax Indication`: Toggle the switch to indicate if the price "
"is :ref:`VAT included or excluded <ecommerce/prices/taxes>`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:127
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Variants`: Show all possible product :ref:`variants <ecommerce/"
"products/product-variants>` vertically as a :guilabel:`Products List` or "
"horizontally as selectable :guilabel:`Options` to compose the variant "
"yourself."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Varian`: Tampilkan semua :ref:`varian <ecommerce/products/product-"
"variants>` produk yang mungkin secara vertikal sebagai :guilabel:`Daftar "
"Produk` atau horizontal sebagai :guilabel:`Opsi` yang dapat dipilih untuk "
"menyusun varian sendiri."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:131
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Product Tags`: Toggle the switch to display "
"the :guilabel:`Product Template Tags` on the product page and allow "
"customers to filter products using those tags."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tag Produk`: Aktifkan tombol untuk menampilkan :guilabel:`Tag "
"Template Produk` pada halaman produk dan memungkinkan pelanggan memfilter "
"produk menggunakan tag tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:134
msgid ":guilabel:`Cart`:"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Keranjang`:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:136
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Buy Now`: Add a :icon:`fa-bolt` :guilabel:`Buy Now` option to "
"take the customer to the checkout page."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Beli Sekarang`: Tambahkan opsi :icon:`fa-bolt` :guilabel:`Beli "
"Sekarang` untuk membawa pelanggan ke halaman checkout."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:138
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Wishlist`: Add an :icon:`fa-heart-o` :guilabel:`Add to wishlist` "
"option allowing logged-in customers to save products in a wishlist."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Wishlist`: Tambahkan opsi :icon:`fa-heart-o` :guilabel:`Tambahkan "
"ke wishlist` yang memungkinkan pelanggan yang sudah login untuk menyimpan "
"produk dalam wishlist."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:140
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Compare`: Add a :icon:`fa-exchange` :guilabel:`Compare` option, "
"allowing customers to :ref:`compare products <ecommerce/products/product-"
"comparison>` based on their attributes."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Bandingkan`: Tambahkan opsi :icon:`fa-exchange` "
":guilabel:`Bandingkan`, yang memungkinkan pelanggan untuk "
":ref:`membandingkan produk <ecommerce/products/product-comparison>` "
"berdasarkan atribut mereka."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:143
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Specification`: Select :guilabel:`Bottom of Page` to display a "
"detailed list of the attributes and their values available for the product. "
"This option only works for products with :ref:`variants <ecommerce/products/"
"product-variants>` if the :ref:`Product comparison tool <ecommerce/products/"
"product-comparison>` is enabled in the Website :guilabel:`Settings`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Spesifikasi`: Pilih :guilabel:`Bagian Bawah Halaman` untuk "
"menampilkan daftar detail atribut dan nilainya yang tersedia untuk produk. "
"Opsi ini hanya berfungsi untuk produk dengan :ref:`varian <ecommerce/"
"products/product-variants>` jika :ref:`Alat perbandingan produk <ecommerce/"
"products/product-comparison>` diaktifkan di :guilabel:`Pengaturan` Website."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:150
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Variants`, :icon:`fa-heart-o` :guilabel:`Wishlist`, and :icon:`fa-"
"exchange` :guilabel:`Compare` options must be enabled by going "
"to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings`, in "
"the :guilabel:`Shop - Products` section."
msgstr ""
"Opsi :guilabel:`Varian`, :icon:`fa-heart-o` :guilabel:`Wishlist`, dan "
":icon:`fa-exchange` :guilabel:`Bandingkan` harus diaktifkan dengan membuka "
":menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings`, di bagian "
":guilabel:`Shop - Products`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:154
msgid "Enabled functions apply to all product pages."
msgstr "Fungsi yang diaktifkan berlaku untuk semua halaman produk."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:155
msgid ""
"Products with single values for their attributes do not generate variants "
"but are still displayed in the :guilabel:`Product Specifications`."
msgstr ""
"Produk dengan nilai tunggal untuk atributnya tidak menghasilkan varian "
"tetapi tetap ditampilkan di :guilabel:`Spesifikasi Produk`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:161
msgid "Product images and videos"
msgstr "Gambar dan video produk"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:163
msgid ""
"To add more media items, such as images and videos, navigate to "
"the :ref:`product form <ecommerce/products/product-form>`, then go to "
"the :guilabel:`Sales` tab and click :guilabel:`Add Media` under "
"the :guilabel:`Ecommerce Media` section. In the :guilabel:`Select a media` "
"pop-up window, go to the :guilabel:`Images` tab, select an image, "
"click :guilabel:`Upload an image` or :guilabel:`Add URL`. Or navigate to "
"the :guilabel:`Videos` tab, paste a video URL or embed code. Once done, "
"click :guilabel:`Add`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menambahkan lebih banyak item media, seperti gambar dan video, buka "
":ref:`formulir produk <ecommerce/products/product-form>`, kemudian buka tab "
":guilabel:`Sales` dan klik :guilabel:`Tambahkan Media` di bawah bagian "
":guilabel:`Ecommerce Media`. Di jendela pop-up :guilabel:`Pilih media`, buka "
"tab :guilabel:`Gambar`, pilih gambar, klik :guilabel:`Unggah gambar` atau "
":guilabel:`Tambahkan URL`. Atau buka tab :guilabel:`Video`, tempelkan URL "
"video atau kode embed. Setelah selesai, klik :guilabel:`Tambahkan`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:170
msgid ""
"To customize the images or videos, go to the ecommerce product page, "
"click :guilabel:`Edit` and select the relevant media. In "
"the :guilabel:`Customize` tab, use the following features:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk menyesuaikan gambar atau video, buka halaman produk eCommerce, klik "
":guilabel:`Edit` dan pilih media yang relevan. Di tab :guilabel:`Sesuaikan`, "
"gunakan fitur-fitur berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:173
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Images Width`: Changes the width of the product images displayed "
"on the page."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Lebar Gambar`: Mengubah lebar gambar produk yang ditampilkan di "
"halaman."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:174
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Layout`: The :guilabel:`Carousel` layout allows customers to "
"navigate from one image to the next using the :icon:`fa-angle-left` "
"(:guilabel:`left arrow`) or :icon:`fa-angle-right` (:guilabel:`right "
"arrow`); whereas the :guilabel:`Grid` displays four images in a square "
"layout."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tata Letak`: Tata letak :guilabel:`Carousel` memungkinkan "
"pelanggan untuk berpindah dari satu gambar ke gambar berikutnya menggunakan "
":icon:`fa-angle-left` (:guilabel:`panah kiri`) atau :icon:`fa-angle-right` "
"(:guilabel:`panah kanan`); sedangkan :guilabel:`Grid` menampilkan empat "
"gambar dalam tata letak persegi."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:177
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Image Zoom`: Select the zoom effect for product "
"images: :guilabel:`Magnifier on hover` :guilabel:`Pop-up on "
"Click`, :guilabel:`Both`, or :guilabel:`None`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Zoom Gambar`: Pilih efek zoom untuk gambar produk: "
":guilabel:`Pembesar saat diarahkan`, :guilabel:`Pop-up saat Diklik`, "
":guilabel:`Keduanya`, atau :guilabel:`Tidak Ada`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:179
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Thumbnails`: Align thumbnails on the :icon:`fa-long-arrow-left` "
"(:guilabel:`Left`) or at the :icon:`fa-long-arrow-down` (:guilabel:`Bottom`)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Thumbnail`: Sejajarkan thumbnail di :icon:`fa-long-arrow-left` "
"(:guilabel:`Kiri`) atau di :icon:`fa-long-arrow-down` (:guilabel:`Bawah`)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:182
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Main Image`: Click :guilabel:`Replace` to change the product's "
"main image."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Gambar Utama`: Klik :guilabel:`Ganti` untuk mengubah gambar utama "
"produk."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:183
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Extra Images`: :guilabel:`Add` more extra images or videos "
"(including via URL) or :guilabel:`Remove all`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Gambar Tambahan`: :guilabel:`Tambahkan` lebih banyak gambar atau "
"video tambahan (termasuk melalui URL) atau :guilabel:`Hapus semua`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:187
msgid ""
"Images must be in PNG or JPG format, with at least one dimension (height or "
"width) greater than 1024 pixels to trigger the zoom."
msgstr ""
"Gambar harus dalam format PNG atau JPG, dengan setidaknya satu dimensi "
"(tinggi atau lebar) lebih besar dari 1024 piksel untuk memicu zoom."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:193
msgid "Products block"
msgstr "Blok produk"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:195
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Products` :doc:`building block <../website/web_design/"
"building_blocks>` is used to display a selection of products sold on your "
"website."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Blok bangunan` :doc:`Products <../website/web_design/"
"building_blocks>` digunakan untuk menampilkan pilihan produk yang dijual di "
"website Anda."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:None
msgid "Example of a products block"
msgstr "Contoh blok produk"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:201
msgid ""
"By default, the block displays the :guilabel:`Newest Products`. To change "
"which products are shown, go to the :guilabel:`Customize` "
"tab's :guilabel:`Products` section and set the :guilabel:`Filter` field "
"to :guilabel:`Recently Sold Products` or :guilabel:`Recently Viewed "
"Products`."
msgstr ""
"Secara default, blok menampilkan :guilabel:`Produk Terbaru`. Untuk mengubah "
"produk yang ditampilkan, buka bagian :guilabel:`Products` di tab "
":guilabel:`Sesuaikan` dan atur field :guilabel:`Filter` ke :guilabel:`Produk "
"yang Baru Terjual` atau :guilabel:`Produk yang Baru Dilihat`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:205
msgid ""
"In addition, it is possible to display products from a specific category "
"only using the :guilabel:`Category` field."
msgstr ""
"Selain itu, dimungkinkan untuk menampilkan produk dari kategori tertentu "
"saja menggunakan field :guilabel:`Kategori`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:208
msgid ""
"You can also filter products by :guilabel:`Tags`, "
"include :guilabel:`Variants`, and adjust the display by selecting a "
"different :guilabel:`Template`."
msgstr ""
"Anda juga dapat memfilter produk berdasarkan :guilabel:`Tag`, menyertakan "
":guilabel:`Varian`, dan menyesuaikan tampilan dengan memilih "
":guilabel:`Template` yang berbeda."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:214
msgid "Product variants"
msgstr "Varian-varian produk"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:216
msgid ""
":doc:`Product variants <../../sales/sales/products_prices/products/"
"variants>` are different versions of the same product, such as various "
"colors or materials, with potential differences in price and availability."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Varian produk <../../sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants>` "
"adalah versi berbeda dari produk yang sama, seperti berbagai warna atau "
"bahan, dengan kemungkinan perbedaan harga dan ketersediaan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:220
msgid "To configure product variants for a product:"
msgstr "Untuk mengonfigurasi varian produk untuk suatu produk:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:222
#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:104
#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:26
#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:136
msgid "Go to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings`."
msgstr "Buka :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:223
msgid ""
"Scroll down to the :guilabel:`Shop - Products` section and enable "
"the :guilabel:`Product Variants` feature."
msgstr ""
"Gulir ke bawah ke bagian :guilabel:`Shop - Products` dan aktifkan fitur "
":guilabel:`Product Variants`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:225
msgid ""
"Access the :ref:`product forms <ecommerce/products/product-form>` and go to "
"the :guilabel:`Attributes & Variants` tab, where you can add attributes and "
"values, allowing customers to configure and select product variants on the "
"product page. For multiple attributes, you can combine them to create "
"specific variants."
msgstr ""
"Akses :ref:`formulir produk <ecommerce/products/product-form>` dan buka tab "
":guilabel:`Attributes & Variants`, di mana Anda dapat menambahkan atribut "
"dan nilai, memungkinkan pelanggan untuk mengonfigurasi dan memilih varian "
"produk pada halaman produk. Untuk beberapa atribut, Anda dapat "
"menggabungkannya untuk membuat varian tertentu."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:230
msgid ""
"To display or hide an attribute on the :guilabel:`Shop` page and allow "
"visitors to filter them, go to :menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce --> "
"Attributes`, click on the attribute, and select :guilabel:`Visible` "
"or :guilabel:`Hidden` in the :guilabel:`eCommerce Filter Visibility` field."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menampilkan atau menyembunyikan atribut pada halaman :guilabel:`Shop` "
"dan mengizinkan pengunjung untuk memfilternya, buka "
":menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce --> Attributes`, klik atribut "
"tersebut, dan pilih :guilabel:`Visible` atau :guilabel:`Hidden` di bidang "
":guilabel:`eCommerce Filter Visibility`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:235
msgid ""
"To display the product attributes in the :doc:`product catalog <products/"
"catalog>`, set the :guilabel:`Attributes` feature to :guilabel:`Left` using "
"the website editor."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menampilkan atribut produk di :doc:`product catalog <products/catalog>"
"`, atur fitur :guilabel:`Attributes` ke :guilabel:`Left` menggunakan website "
"editor."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:237
msgid ""
"To group attributes under the same section when :ref:`comparing products "
"<ecommerce/products/product-comparison>`, go to the :guilabel:`eCommerce "
"Category` field and either select an :doc:`existing category or create a new "
"one <../../websites/ecommerce/products>`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengelompokkan atribut di bawah bagian yang sama saat "
":ref:`membandingkan produk <ecommerce/products/product-comparison>`, buka "
"bidang :guilabel:`eCommerce Category` dan pilih :doc:`kategori yang ada atau "
"buat yang baru <../../websites/ecommerce/products>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:243
msgid "Two attribute values are needed to make the filter visible."
msgstr "Dua nilai atribut diperlukan untuk membuat filter terlihat."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:246
msgid ""
":doc:`Product variants <../../sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants>`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`Varian produk <../../sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants>`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:251
msgid "Digital files"
msgstr "File digital"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:253
msgid ""
"You can link digital files like certificates, eBooks, or user manuals to the "
"products. These documents are available :ref:`before payment <ecommerce-"
"products-digital-files-before-payment>` on the product page or in the "
"customer portal :ref:`after checkout <ecommerce-products-digital-files-after-"
"payment>`."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat menghubungkan file digital seperti sertifikat, eBook, atau manual "
"pengguna ke produk. Dokumen-dokumen ini tersedia :ref:`sebelum pembayaran "
"<ecommerce-products-digital-files-before-payment>` pada halaman produk atau "
"di portal pelanggan :ref:`setelah checkout <ecommerce-products-digital-files-"
"after-payment>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:258
msgid ""
"To link a digital file to a product, go to the :ref:`product form <ecommerce/"
"products/product-form>` and click the :guilabel:`Documents` smart button. "
"Then, click :guilabel:`Upload` to upload a file directly, or for additional "
"options, click :guilabel:`New`, then :guilabel:`Upload your file`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menghubungkan file digital ke produk, buka :ref:`formulir produk "
"<ecommerce/products/product-form>` dan klik tombol pintar "
":guilabel:`Dokumen`. Kemudian, klik :guilabel:`Upload` untuk mengunggah file "
"secara langsung, atau untuk opsi tambahan, klik :guilabel:`New`, lalu "
":guilabel:`Upload your file`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:263
msgid ""
"You can link a URL instead of a digital file. To do so, "
"click :guilabel:`New`, go to the :guilabel:`Type` field, and "
"select :guilabel:`URL`."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat menghubungkan URL alih-alih file digital. Untuk melakukannya, "
"klik :guilabel:`New`, buka bidang :guilabel:`Type`, dan pilih "
":guilabel:`URL`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:265
msgid ""
"To edit an existing file, click the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` "
"(:guilabel:`dropdown menu`) in the top-right corner of the document card and "
"click :guilabel:`Edit`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengedit file yang ada, klik :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` (:guilabel:`menu "
"dropdown`) di sudut kanan atas kartu dokumen dan klik :guilabel:`Edit`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:271
msgid "Digital files available before payment"
msgstr "File digital yang tersedia sebelum pembayaran"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:273
msgid ""
"To make the file available on the product page (before payment), leave "
"the :guilabel:`Visibility` field blank and toggle the :guilabel:`Show on "
"product page` switch."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat file tersedia pada halaman produk (sebelum pembayaran), "
"biarkan bidang :guilabel:`Visibility` kosong dan aktifkan tombol "
":guilabel:`Show on product page`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:None
msgid "digital file available before payment on the  product page"
msgstr "file digital yang tersedia sebelum pembayaran pada halaman produk"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:282
msgid "Digital files available after payment"
msgstr "File digital yang tersedia setelah pembayaran"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:284
msgid ""
"To make the file available (after payment), set the :guilabel:`Visibility` "
"field to :guilabel:`Confirmed order` and turn off the :guilabel:`Show on "
"product page` switch."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat file tersedia (setelah pembayaran), atur bidang "
":guilabel:`Visibility` ke :guilabel:`Confirmed order` dan matikan tombol "
":guilabel:`Show on product page`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:290
msgid "Translation"
msgstr "Terjemahan"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:292
msgid ""
"If multiple languages are available on your website, you can translate a "
"product's information directly on the :ref:`product form <ecommerce/products/"
"product-form>`. Fields that support multiple languages are identifiable by "
"their abbreviation language (e.g., EN) next to their field."
msgstr ""
"Jika beberapa bahasa tersedia di website Anda, Anda dapat menerjemahkan "
"informasi produk secara langsung pada :ref:`formulir produk <ecommerce/"
"products/product-form>`. Bidang yang mendukung beberapa bahasa dapat "
"diidentifikasi dari singkatan bahasa (misalnya, EN) di samping bidangnya."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:296
msgid "The eCommerce-related fields to translate are:"
msgstr "Bidang terkait eCommerce yang perlu diterjemahkan adalah:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:298
msgid ":guilabel:`Product name`."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Nama produk`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:299
msgid ":guilabel:`Out-of-Stock Message` (under the :guilabel:`Sales` tab)."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Pesan Stok Habis` (di bawah tab :guilabel:`Sales`)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:300
msgid ":guilabel:`Sales Description` (under the :guilabel:`Sales` tab)."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Deskripsi Penjualan` (di bawah tab :guilabel:`Sales`)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:303
msgid ""
"Having untranslated content on a web page may be detrimental to the user "
"experience and :doc:`SEO <../../websites/website/structure/seo>`. You can "
"use the :doc:`Translate <../website/configuration/translate>` feature to "
"translate the page's content."
msgstr ""
"Memiliki konten yang tidak diterjemahkan di halaman web dapat merugikan "
"pengalaman pengguna dan :doc:`SEO <../../websites/website/structure/seo>`. "
"Anda dapat menggunakan fitur :doc:`Translate <../website/configuration/"
"translate>` untuk menerjemahkan konten halaman."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:306
msgid ""
"To check the language(s) of your website, go to :menuselection:`Website --> "
"Configuration --> Settings` and go to the :guilabel:`Website Info` section."
msgstr ""
"Untuk memeriksa bahasa situs web Anda, buka :menuselection:`Website --> "
"Configuration --> Settings` dan buka bagian :guilabel:`Website Info`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:312
msgid "Website availability"
msgstr "Ketersediaan situs web"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:314
msgid ""
"To set the product's website availability, navigate to the :ref:`product "
"form <ecommerce/products/product-form>`, go to the :guilabel:`Sales` tab, "
"and in the :guilabel:`eCommerce shop` section, select "
"the :guilabel:`Website` you wish the product to be available on. Leave the "
"field blank to make the product available on *all* websites."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengatur ketersediaan produk di situs web, buka :ref:`formulir produk "
"<ecommerce/products/product-form>`, buka tab :guilabel:`Sales`, dan di "
"bagian :guilabel:`eCommerce shop`, pilih :guilabel:`Website` tempat Anda "
"ingin produk tersedia. Biarkan kolom kosong untuk membuat produk tersedia di "
"*semua* situs web."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:320
msgid ""
"You can make a product available on either *one* website or *all* websites, "
"but selecting only *some* websites is not possible."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat membuat produk tersedia di *satu* situs web atau *semua* situs "
"web, tetapi memilih hanya *beberapa* situs web tidak memungkinkan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:326
msgid "Stock management"
msgstr "Manajemen stok"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:328
msgid ""
"To enable and configure inventory management options, go "
"to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings`, scroll down to "
"the :guilabel:`Shop - Products` section and the :guilabel:`Inventory "
"Defaults` sub-section."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengaktifkan dan mengonfigurasi opsi manajemen inventaris, buka "
":menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings`, gulir ke bawah ke "
"bagian :guilabel:`Shop - Products` dan sub-bagian :guilabel:`Inventory "
"Defaults`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:333
msgid ""
"The **Inventory** app must be installed to see the inventory management "
"options."
msgstr ""
"Aplikasi **Inventaris** harus diinstal untuk melihat opsi manajemen "
"inventaris."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:334
msgid ""
"To display the stock level on the product page, the :guilabel:`Product Type` "
"field must be set to :guilabel:`Storable` in the :ref:`product form "
"<ecommerce/products/product-form>`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menampilkan tingkat stok di halaman produk, kolom :guilabel:`Product "
"Type` harus diatur ke :guilabel:`Storable` di :ref:`formulir produk "
"<ecommerce/products/product-form>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:338
msgid "Inventory"
msgstr "Stok Persediaan"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:340
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Inventory Defaults` sub-section, fill in those fields:"
msgstr "Di sub-bagian :guilabel:`Inventory Defaults`, isi kolom-kolom berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:342
msgid ""
":doc:`Warehouse <../../inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/"
"inventory_management/warehouses>`."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Gudang <../../inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/"
"inventory_management/warehouses>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:343
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Out-of-Stock`: Enable :guilabel:`Continue Selling` to allow "
"customers to place orders even when the product is **out of stock**. Leave "
"the box unchecked to **prevent orders**."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Out-of-Stock`: Aktifkan :guilabel:`Continue Selling` untuk "
"memungkinkan pelanggan melakukan pemesanan meskipun produk **stok habis**. "
"Biarkan kotak tidak dicentang untuk **mencegah pemesanan**."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:345
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Show Available Qty`: Displays the available quantity left under a "
"specified threshold on the product page. The available quantity is "
"calculated based on the :guilabel:`On hand` quantity minus the quantity "
"already reserved for outgoing transfers."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Show Available Qty`: Menampilkan jumlah yang tersedia di bawah "
"ambang batas yang ditentukan di halaman produk. Jumlah yang tersedia "
"dihitung berdasarkan jumlah :guilabel:`On hand` dikurangi jumlah yang sudah "
"dipesan untuk transfer keluar."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:352
msgid "Product comparison"
msgstr "Perbandingan produk"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:354
msgid ""
"To allow website visitors to compare products based on their attributes, go "
"to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings`, scroll down to "
"the :guilabel:`Shop - Products` section, and enable :guilabel:`Product "
"Comparison Tool`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk memungkinkan pengunjung situs web membandingkan produk berdasarkan "
"atributnya, buka :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings`, "
"gulir ke bawah ke bagian :guilabel:`Shop - Products`, dan aktifkan "
":guilabel:`Product Comparison Tool`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:358
msgid ""
"The :icon:`fa-exchange` (:guilabel:`Compare`) icon is now available on each "
"product card on the main shop page when customers hover their mouse over it. "
"To compare products, customers can click the :icon:`fa-exchange` "
"(:guilabel:`Compare`) option on the products they want to compare, then "
"click :icon:`fa-exchange` :guilabel:`Compare` in the pop-up window at the "
"bottom of the page to reach the comparison summary."
msgstr ""
"Ikon :icon:`fa-exchange` (:guilabel:`Compare`) sekarang tersedia di setiap "
"kartu produk di halaman toko utama ketika pelanggan mengarahkan mouse ke "
"atasnya. Untuk membandingkan produk, pelanggan dapat mengklik opsi :icon:`fa-"
"exchange` (:guilabel:`Compare`) pada produk yang ingin mereka bandingkan, "
"lalu klik :icon:`fa-exchange` :guilabel:`Compare` di jendela pop-up di "
"bagian bawah halaman untuk membuka ringkasan perbandingan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:None
msgid "Product comparison window"
msgstr "Jendela perbandingan produk"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:368
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Product Comparison Tool` is only available for products "
"with :ref:`attributes <ecommerce/products/product-variants>`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Product Comparison Tool` hanya tersedia untuk produk dengan "
":ref:`atribut <ecommerce/products/product-variants>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:370
msgid ""
"Selecting the :icon:`fa-exchange` (:guilabel:`Compare`) option from a "
"product page is also possible."
msgstr ""
"Memilih opsi :icon:`fa-exchange` (:guilabel:`Compare`) dari halaman produk "
"juga memungkinkan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:376
msgid "Wishlists"
msgstr "Wishlist"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:378
msgid ""
"The :icon:`fa-heart-o` :guilabel:`Add to wishlist` button allows customers "
"to add products to their wishlist, i.e., save them for later. To enable it, "
"go to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings`, scroll down "
"to the :guilabel:`Shop - Products` section, and "
"enable :guilabel:`Wishlists`. The button is available on each product page "
"and can be disabled in the :ref:`website editor <ecommerce/products/product-"
"page>` if needed."
msgstr ""
"Tombol :icon:`fa-heart-o` :guilabel:`Add to wishlist` memungkinkan pelanggan "
"menambahkan produk ke wishlist mereka, yaitu menyimpannya untuk nanti. Untuk "
"mengaktifkannya, buka :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> "
"Settings`, gulir ke bawah ke bagian :guilabel:`Shop - Products`, dan "
"aktifkan :guilabel:`Wishlists`. Tombol tersebut tersedia pada setiap halaman "
"produk dan dapat dinonaktifkan di :ref:`website editor <ecommerce/products/"
"product-page>` jika diperlukan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:None
msgid "Add to wishlist button"
msgstr "Tombol tambahkan ke wishlist"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:388
msgid ""
"You can also display a :icon:`fa-heart-o` (:guilabel:`Wishlist`) button when "
"hovering the mouse over the product on the :ref:`shop page <ecommerce/"
"catalog/additional-features>`."
msgstr ""
"Anda juga dapat menampilkan tombol :icon:`fa-heart-o` (:guilabel:`Wishlist`) "
"saat mengarahkan mouse ke produk di :ref:`shop page <ecommerce/catalog/"
"additional-features>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:390
msgid ""
"Customers can move products from their cart to their wishlist by clicking "
"the :guilabel:`Save for later` button in the :guilabel:`Order "
"overview` :ref:`checkout step <ecommerce/checkout/review_order>`."
msgstr ""
"Pelanggan dapat memindahkan produk dari keranjang mereka ke wishlist dengan "
"mengklik tombol :guilabel:`Save for later` di :guilabel:`Order overview` "
":ref:`checkout step <ecommerce/checkout/review_order>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:3
msgid "Catalog"
msgstr "Katalog"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:5
msgid ""
"The eCommerce catalog displays products for customers to browse. It is "
"organized using product categories, available options, sorting, and "
"navigation paths. Essentially, the eCommerce catalog is the shop page of "
"your website."
msgstr ""
"Katalog eCommerce menampilkan produk untuk dijelajahi pelanggan. Katalog ini "
"diorganisir menggunakan kategori produk, opsi yang tersedia, pengurutan, dan "
"jalur navigasi. Pada dasarnya, katalog eCommerce adalah halaman toko dari "
"website Anda."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:9
msgid ""
"The product catalog includes a :ref:`top bar <ecommerce/catalog/top-bar>`, "
"a :ref:`side panel <ecommerce/catalog/side-panel>`, and a :ref:`product "
"listing area <ecommerce/catalog/product-listing>`. With Odoo, you "
"can :ref:`customize the layout <ecommerce/catalog/customize-layout>`, filter "
"by :ref:`categories and attributes <ecommerce/catalog/categories>`, and "
"use :ref:`additional features <ecommerce/catalog/additional-features>` "
"according to your needs."
msgstr ""
"Katalog produk mencakup :ref:`bilah atas <ecommerce/catalog/top-bar>`, "
":ref:`panel samping <ecommerce/catalog/side-panel>`, dan :ref:`area daftar "
"produk <ecommerce/catalog/product-listing>`. Dengan Odoo, Anda dapat "
":ref:`menyesuaikan tata letak <ecommerce/catalog/customize-layout>`, "
"memfilter berdasarkan :ref:`kategori dan atribut <ecommerce/catalog/"
"categories>`, dan menggunakan :ref:`fitur tambahan <ecommerce/catalog/"
"additional-features>` sesuai kebutuhan Anda."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:16
msgid ""
"You can customize the shop page using the website editor. To access it, go "
"to the shop page, click :guilabel:`Edit` in the upper-right corner, and "
"navigate to the :guilabel:`Customize` tab."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat menyesuaikan halaman toko menggunakan editor website. Untuk "
"mengaksesnya, buka halaman toko, klik :guilabel:`Edit` di pojok kanan atas, "
"dan navigasi ke tab :guilabel:`Customize`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:22
msgid "Top bar"
msgstr "Bilah atas"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:24
msgid ""
"The top bar can include a search bar, a currency selector, :ref:`sort-by and "
"display options <ecommerce/catalog/sort-by-and-display-option>`, "
"and :ref:`category quick access <ecommerce/catalog/categories>`."
msgstr ""
"Bilah atas dapat mencakup bilah pencarian, pemilih mata uang, :ref:`opsi "
"urutkan berdasarkan dan tampilan <ecommerce/catalog/sort-by-and-display-"
"option>`, serta :ref:`akses cepat kategori <ecommerce/catalog/categories>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:31
msgid "Sort-by search and display options"
msgstr "Opsi pencarian urutkan berdasarkan dan tampilan"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:33
msgid ""
"You can toggle the :guilabel:`Search Bar`, display :ref:`categories "
"<ecommerce/catalog/categories>` and/or :ref:`attributes <ecommerce/catalog/"
"attributes>`, and enable or disable the :guilabel:`Sort-By` as well as "
"the :ref:`Layout <ecommerce/catalog/layout>` buttons in the :guilabel:`Top "
"Bar`."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat mengaktifkan/nonaktifkan :guilabel:`Search Bar`, menampilkan "
":ref:`kategori <ecommerce/catalog/categories>` dan/atau :ref:`atribut "
"<ecommerce/catalog/attributes>`, dan mengaktifkan atau menonaktifkan tombol "
":guilabel:`Sort-By` serta :ref:`Layout <ecommerce/catalog/layout>` di "
":guilabel:`Top Bar`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:38
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Sort-by` button is toggled by default, and customers can "
"choose between the following :guilabel:`Default Sort` options:"
msgstr ""
"Tombol :guilabel:`Sort-by` diaktifkan secara default, dan pelanggan dapat "
"memilih di antara opsi :guilabel:`Default Sort` berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:41
msgid ":guilabel:`None`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`None`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:42
msgid ":guilabel:`Featured`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Featured`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:43
msgid ":guilabel:`Newest Arrivals`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Newest Arrivals`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:44
msgid ":guilabel:`Name (A-Z)`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Name (A-Z)`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:45
msgid ":guilabel:`Price - Low to High`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Price - Low to High`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:46
msgid ":guilabel:`Price - High to Low`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Price - High to Low`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:48
msgid ""
"The default sort applies to *all* :ref:`categories <ecommerce/catalog/"
"categories>`."
msgstr ""
"Pengurutan default berlaku untuk *semua* :ref:`kategori <ecommerce/catalog/"
"categories>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:51
msgid ""
"If you don't want to display a top bar or :ref:`side panel <ecommerce/"
"catalog/side-panel>`, you can disable all related options in the website "
"editor."
msgstr ""
"Jika Anda tidak ingin menampilkan bilah atas atau :ref:`panel samping "
"<ecommerce/catalog/side-panel>`, Anda dapat menonaktifkan semua opsi terkait "
"di editor website."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:57
msgid "Side panel"
msgstr "Panel samping"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:59
msgid ""
"The side panel provides advanced filtering tools to organize your product "
"categories. To further :ref:`categorize <ecommerce/catalog/categories>` the "
"shop page, you can activate various filters, such as the :ref:`attribute "
"<ecommerce/catalog/attributes>` filter."
msgstr ""
"Panel samping menyediakan alat pemfilteran lanjutan untuk mengorganisir "
"kategori produk Anda. Untuk lebih lanjut :ref:`mengkategorikan <ecommerce/"
"catalog/categories>` halaman toko, Anda dapat mengaktifkan berbagai filter, "
"seperti filter :ref:`atribut <ecommerce/catalog/attributes>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:63
msgid ""
"You can also add a :guilabel:`Datepicker` option to display a date range "
"calendar to check the availability of rental products over a specific "
"period. The :doc:`Rental app <../../../sales/rental>` must be installed to "
"use this feature."
msgstr ""
"Anda juga dapat menambahkan opsi :guilabel:`Datepicker` untuk menampilkan "
"kalender rentang tanggal guna memeriksa ketersediaan produk rental dalam "
"periode tertentu. Aplikasi :doc:`Rental <../../../sales/rental>` harus "
"diinstal untuk menggunakan fitur ini."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:67
msgid ""
"It is also possible to toggle the :guilabel:`Collapsible sidebar` switch to "
"make the side panel manually collapsible."
msgstr ""
"Dimungkinkan juga untuk mengaktifkan/nonaktifkan sakelar "
":guilabel:`Collapsible sidebar` agar panel samping dapat dilipat secara "
"manual."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:71
msgid ""
"To use a price range or tags filter, you have to enable :ref:`attributes "
"<ecommerce/catalog/attributes>` first."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menggunakan filter rentang harga atau tag, Anda harus mengaktifkan "
":ref:`atribut <ecommerce/catalog/attributes>` terlebih dahulu."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:77
msgid "Product categorization in catalog"
msgstr "Kategorisasi produk dalam katalog"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:79
msgid ""
"eCommerce categories are used to organize products into groups, making it "
"easier for customers to browse the online store."
msgstr ""
"Kategori eCommerce digunakan untuk mengatur produk ke dalam grup, memudahkan "
"pelanggan menjelajahi toko online."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:82
msgid ""
"To create eCommerce categories, go to :menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce "
"--> eCommerce Categories`, and click :guilabel:`New`. On the category form, "
"add a :guilabel:`Name`, optionally enter a :guilabel:`Parent Category`, and "
"write a :guilabel:`Category Description`, if needed."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat kategori eCommerce, buka :menuselection:`Website --> "
"eCommerce --> eCommerce Categories`, lalu klik :guilabel:`New`. Pada "
"formulir kategori, tambahkan :guilabel:`Name`, secara opsional masukkan "
":guilabel:`Parent Category`, dan tulis :guilabel:`Category Description` jika "
"diperlukan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:87
msgid ""
"To use eCommerce categories, go to :menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce --> "
"Products`, select the product you wish to modify, go to "
"the :guilabel:`Sales` tab, navigate to the :guilabel:`Ecommerce shop` "
"section, and select the :guilabel:`Categories` it belongs to."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menggunakan kategori eCommerce, buka :menuselection:`Website --> "
"eCommerce --> Products`, pilih produk yang ingin diubah, buka tab "
":guilabel:`Sales`, navigasi ke bagian :guilabel:`Ecommerce shop`, dan pilih "
":guilabel:`Categories` yang menjadi tempatnya."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:92
msgid "A single product can belong to multiple eCommerce categories."
msgstr "Satu produk dapat termasuk dalam beberapa kategori eCommerce."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:94
msgid ""
"Once the categories are configured and assigned to the relevant products, go "
"to the main shop page and open the website editor. In "
"the :guilabel:`Categories` option, you can either enable a menu on "
"the :guilabel:`Left`, i.e., in the :ref:`side panel <ecommerce/catalog/side-"
"panel>`, or on the :guilabel:`Top`, i.e., in the :ref:`top bar <ecommerce/"
"catalog/top-bar>`, or both. If you select the :guilabel:`Left` category, the "
"option :guilabel:`Collapsible Category Recursive` appears, allowing you to "
"collapse the category in the side panel."
msgstr ""
"Setelah kategori dikonfigurasi dan ditetapkan ke produk yang relevan, buka "
"halaman toko utama dan buka editor website. Dalam opsi "
":guilabel:`Categories`, Anda dapat mengaktifkan menu di :guilabel:`Left`, "
"yaitu di :ref:`panel samping <ecommerce/catalog/side-panel>`, atau di "
":guilabel:`Top`, yaitu di :ref:`bilah atas <ecommerce/catalog/top-bar>`, "
"atau keduanya. Jika Anda memilih kategori :guilabel:`Left`, opsi "
":guilabel:`Collapsible Category Recursive` muncul, memungkinkan Anda "
"menciutkan kategori di panel samping."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:None
msgid "Categories options for your eCommerce website"
msgstr "Opsi kategori untuk situs web eCommerce Anda"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:105
msgid ":doc:`../products`"
msgstr ":doc:`../products`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:110
msgid "Attributes"
msgstr "Atribut"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:112
msgid ""
"Attributes refer to characteristics of a product, such as the color or "
"material, whereas variants are the different combinations of attributes. To "
"configure attributes and variants, go to :menuselection:`Website --> "
"eCommerce --> Products`, select a product, and click "
"the :guilabel:`Attributes & Variants` tab. Add as many attributes as desired."
msgstr ""
"Atribut merujuk pada karakteristik produk, seperti warna atau bahan, "
"sedangkan varian adalah kombinasi berbeda dari atribut. Untuk mengonfigurasi "
"atribut dan varian, buka :menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce --> "
"Products`, pilih produk, dan klik tab :guilabel:`Attributes & Variants`. "
"Tambahkan atribut sebanyak yang diinginkan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:118
msgid ":doc:`../../../sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../../sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:None
msgid "Attributes and variants of your product"
msgstr "Atribut dan varian produk Anda"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:123
msgid ""
"To enable attribute filtering, go to your main shop page, then open the "
"website editor, and set the :guilabel:`Attributes` field to :guilabel:`Left` "
"(:ref:`side panel <ecommerce/catalog/side-panel>`) and/or :guilabel:`Top` "
"(:ref:`top bar <ecommerce/catalog/top-bar>`)."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengaktifkan filter atribut, buka halaman toko utama Anda, lalu buka "
"editor website, dan atur bidang :guilabel:`Attributes` ke :guilabel:`Left` "
"(:ref:`panel samping <ecommerce/catalog/side-panel>`) dan/atau "
":guilabel:`Top` (:ref:`bilah atas <ecommerce/catalog/top-bar>`)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:129
msgid ""
"When attribute filtering is enabled in the top bar, customers must click "
"the :icon:`fa-sliders` (:guilabel:`dropdown toggle`) button to access it."
msgstr ""
"Ketika filter atribut diaktifkan di bilah atas, pelanggan harus mengklik "
"tombol :icon:`fa-sliders` (:guilabel:`dropdown toggle`) untuk mengaksesnya."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:132
msgid "When enabling :guilabel:`Attributes`, more options become available:"
msgstr "Saat mengaktifkan :guilabel:`Attributes`, lebih banyak opsi tersedia:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:134
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Price Filter`: Toggle the switch to display a :guilabel:`Price "
"Range` bar, which allows customers to filter products according to a "
"specific price range by dragging adjustable handles."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Filter Harga`: Aktifkan tombol untuk menampilkan bilah "
":guilabel:`Rentang Harga`, yang memungkinkan pelanggan memfilter produk "
"sesuai rentang harga tertentu dengan menyeret pegangan yang dapat "
"disesuaikan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:137
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Product Tags Filter`: Toggle the switch to display "
"the :guilabel:`Product Tags` on the shop page, and allow customers to filter "
"products using those tags by going to the :guilabel:`Tags` section in "
"the :ref:`side panel <ecommerce/catalog/side-panel>`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Product Tags Filter`: Alihkan sakelar untuk menampilkan "
":guilabel:`Product Tags` di halaman toko, dan izinkan pelanggan memfilter "
"produk menggunakan tag tersebut dengan membuka bagian :guilabel:`Tags` di "
":ref:`panel samping <ecommerce/catalog/side-panel>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:142
msgid ""
"If you want to use tags on your e-commerce, go to :menuselection:`eCommerce "
"--> Product Tags` and click :guilabel:`New`. In the :guilabel:`Product "
"Templates` tab of the product tags form, add the products to link to the "
"given tag. You can also add product variants in the :guilabel:`Product "
"Variants` tab and view a summary of all selected products in "
"the :guilabel:`All Products` tab."
msgstr ""
"Jika Anda ingin menggunakan tag di e-commerce Anda, buka "
":menuselection:`eCommerce --> Product Tags` dan klik :guilabel:`New`. Di tab "
":guilabel:`Product Templates` pada formulir tag produk, tambahkan produk "
"untuk ditautkan ke tag yang diberikan. Anda juga dapat menambahkan varian "
"produk di tab :guilabel:`Product Variants` dan melihat ringkasan semua "
"produk yang dipilih di tab :guilabel:`All Products`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:147
msgid ""
"Price filtering works independently from attributes and, therefore, can be "
"enabled on its own, if desired."
msgstr ""
"Filter harga bekerja secara independen dari atribut dan, oleh karena itu, "
"dapat diaktifkan sendiri jika diinginkan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:153
msgid "Product listing area"
msgstr "Area daftar produk"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:155
msgid ""
"You can customize the layout of the entire shop page, as well as that "
"of :ref:`individual category pages <ecommerce/catalog/customize-layout>`."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat menyesuaikan tata letak seluruh halaman toko, serta tata letak "
":ref:`halaman kategori individual <ecommerce/catalog/customize-layout>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:159
msgid ""
"It is also possible to customize individual :ref:`product pages <ecommerce/"
"products/product-form>`."
msgstr ""
"Juga dimungkinkan untuk menyesuaikan :ref:`halaman produk <ecommerce/"
"products/product-form>` individual."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:163
msgid ""
"In the website editor, choose the :ref:`layout <ecommerce/catalog/sort-by-"
"and-display-option>`, and set the default layout to either :guilabel:`Grid` "
"or :guilabel:`List` view."
msgstr ""
"Di editor website, pilih :ref:`tata letak <ecommerce/catalog/sort-by-and-"
"display-option>`, dan atur tata letak default ke tampilan :guilabel:`Grid` "
"atau :guilabel:`List`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:166
msgid "Use the following options to further adjust the layout:"
msgstr "Gunakan opsi berikut untuk menyesuaikan tata letak lebih lanjut:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:168
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Size`: Set the number of products displayed per page and line."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Ukuran`: Atur jumlah produk yang ditampilkan per halaman dan "
"baris."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:169
msgid ":guilabel:`Gap`: Define the gap between the products."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Gap`: Tentukan jarak antara produk."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:170
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Style`: "
"Select :guilabel:`Default`, :guilabel:`Cards`, :guilabel:`Thumbnails`, "
"or :guilabel:`Grid`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Gaya`: Pilih :guilabel:`Default`, :guilabel:`Kartu`, "
":guilabel:`Thumbnail`, atau :guilabel:`Grid`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:172
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Image Size`: Choose the aspect ratio for the product "
"images: :guilabel:`Landscape (4/3)`, :guilabel:`Default "
"(1/1)`, :guilabel:`Portrait (4/5)`, or :guilabel:`Vertical (2/3)`. You can "
"also adjust the display by changing the :guilabel:`Fill` options to fit your "
"design preferences best."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Image Size`: Pilih rasio aspek untuk gambar produk: "
":guilabel:`Landscape (4/3)`, :guilabel:`Default (1/1)`, :guilabel:`Portrait "
"(4/5)`, atau :guilabel:`Vertical (2/3)`. Anda juga dapat menyesuaikan "
"tampilan dengan mengubah opsi :guilabel:`Fill` agar paling sesuai dengan "
"preferensi desain Anda."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:177
msgid ""
"Toggle the :guilabel:`Prod. Desc.` switch to display the product description "
"below the product's name."
msgstr ""
"Alihkan sakelar :guilabel:`Prod. Desc.` untuk menampilkan deskripsi produk "
"di bawah nama produk."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:181
msgid ""
"You can choose the size of the grid, but be aware that displaying too many "
"products may affect performance and page loading speed."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat memilih ukuran grid, tetapi perlu diingat bahwa menampilkan "
"terlalu banyak produk dapat mempengaruhi kinerja dan kecepatan pemuatan "
"halaman."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:184
msgid ""
"In addition, you can manually change a product’s position on the shop page. "
"To do so, go to the main shop page, click the product, and open the website "
"editor. In the :guilabel:`Product` section, you can reorder the products by "
"using the arrows. The `<<` `>>` buttons allow to move the product to the "
"extreme left or right, and `<` `>` allow to move it one row to the left or "
"right."
msgstr ""
"Selain itu, Anda dapat secara manual mengubah posisi produk di halaman toko. "
"Untuk melakukannya, buka halaman toko utama, klik produk, dan buka editor "
"website. Di bagian :guilabel:`Product`, Anda dapat mengurutkan ulang produk "
"dengan menggunakan panah. Tombol `<<` `>>` memungkinkan untuk memindahkan "
"produk ke paling kiri atau kanan, dan `<` `>` memungkinkan untuk "
"memindahkannya satu baris ke kiri atau kanan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:190
msgid ""
"It is also possible to change the products' positions on the shop page by "
"going to :menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce --> Products`, switching to "
"the list view, and dragging and dropping the products within the list."
msgstr ""
"Anda juga dapat mengubah posisi produk di halaman toko dengan membuka "
":menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce --> Products`, beralih ke tampilan "
"daftar, dan menarik lalu melepas produk dalam daftar."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:195
msgid "Product highlight"
msgstr "Highlight produk"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:197
msgid ""
"You can highlight products to make them more visible on the shop page. To do "
"so, go to the website editor and click the product to highlight. In "
"the :guilabel:`Product` section, you can choose the size of the product "
"image by clicking the grid, and you can also add a :guilabel:`Ribbon`. This "
"displays a banner across the product's image, such "
"as :guilabel:`Sale`, :guilabel:`Sold out`, :guilabel:`Out of stock` "
"or :guilabel:`New!`."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat menyorot produk untuk membuatnya lebih terlihat di halaman toko. "
"Untuk melakukannya, buka editor website dan klik produk yang ingin disorot. "
"Di bagian :guilabel:`Product`, Anda dapat memilih ukuran gambar produk "
"dengan mengklik grid, dan Anda juga dapat menambahkan :guilabel:`Ribbon`. "
"Ini menampilkan banner di seluruh gambar produk, seperti :guilabel:`Sale`, "
":guilabel:`Sold out`, :guilabel:`Out of stock`, atau :guilabel:`New!`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:None
msgid "Ribbon highlight"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:206
msgid ""
"To create a new ribbon, click the green :icon:`fa-plus` (:guilabel:`Create`) "
"icon next to the :guilabel:`Ribbon` field. Then add a :guilabel:`Ribbon "
"name`, define its :guilabel:`Position`, and choose a :guilabel:`Background` "
"and a :guilabel:`Text` label. To edit the ribbon, click the :icon:`fa-pencil-"
"square-o` (:guilabel:`Edit`) icon next to the :guilabel:`Ribbon` label."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat ribbon baru, klik ikon hijau :icon:`fa-plus` "
"(:guilabel:`Create`) di sebelah field :guilabel:`Ribbon`. Kemudian tambahkan "
":guilabel:`Ribbon name`, tentukan :guilabel:`Position`, dan pilih "
":guilabel:`Background` dan label :guilabel:`Text`. Untuk mengedit ribbon, "
"klik ikon :icon:`fa-pencil-square-o` (:guilabel:`Edit`) di sebelah label "
":guilabel:`Ribbon`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:None
msgid "Create a new ribbon."
msgstr "Membuat ribbon baru."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:214
msgid "The ribbon is now available for all the eCommerce products."
msgstr "Ribbon sekarang tersedia untuk semua produk eCommerce."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:217
msgid "There are other ways to create a new ribbon:"
msgstr "Ada cara lain untuk membuat ribbon baru:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:219
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce --> Product Ribbons` and "
"click :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr ""
"Buka :menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce --> Product Ribbons` dan klik "
":guilabel:`New`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:220
msgid ""
"Activate the :doc:`developer mode <../../../general/developer_mode>`, access "
"the product form, and under the :guilabel:`Sales` tab, change or create the "
"ribbon in the :guilabel:`Ribbon` field."
msgstr ""
"Aktifkan :doc:`mode pengembang <../../../general/developer_mode>`, akses "
"formulir produk, dan di bawah tab :guilabel:`Sales`, ubah atau buat ribbon "
"di field :guilabel:`Ribbon`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:224
msgid ""
"It is also possible to add ribbons for specific :ref:`product variants "
"<ecommerce/products/product-variants>`. To do so, go "
"to :menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce --> Products` and select a product. "
"Click the :guilabel:`Variants` smart button, choose a variant, and add a "
"ribbon in the :guilabel:`Variant Ribbon` field of the :guilabel:`Sales` "
"section."
msgstr ""
"Anda juga dapat menambahkan ribbon untuk :ref:`varian produk <ecommerce/"
"products/product-variants>` tertentu. Untuk melakukannya, buka "
":menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce --> Products` dan pilih produk. Klik "
"tombol pintar :guilabel:`Variants`, pilih varian, dan tambahkan ribbon di "
"field :guilabel:`Variant Ribbon` pada bagian :guilabel:`Sales`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:233
msgid "Shop and category page design"
msgstr "Desain halaman toko dan kategori"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:235
msgid ""
"Use :doc:`building blocks <../../website/web_design/building_blocks>` to add "
"content on the shop and/or category page."
msgstr ""
"Gunakan :doc:`building block <../../website/web_design/building_blocks>` "
"untuk menambahkan konten di halaman toko dan/atau kategori."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:238
msgid ""
"You can customize the top and/or bottom section of the catalog, either for "
"the entire shop page or for a specific category. In the latter case, the "
"block appears *only* when filtering by that category. To do so, move the "
"block to the far top or bottom section to display it on the general shop "
"page or to the area below the category's name at the top or beneath the "
"product list to display it only when filtering by that specific category."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat menyesuaikan bagian atas dan/atau bawah katalog, baik untuk "
"seluruh halaman toko atau untuk kategori tertentu. Dalam kasus terakhir, "
"blok muncul *hanya* saat memfilter berdasarkan kategori tersebut. Untuk "
"melakukannya, pindahkan blok ke bagian paling atas atau bawah untuk "
"menampilkannya di halaman toko umum atau ke area di bawah nama kategori di "
"bagian atas atau di bawah daftar produk untuk menampilkannya hanya saat "
"memfilter berdasarkan kategori spesifik tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:0
msgid "Place building block in the header or footer."
msgstr "Tempatkan blok bangunan di header atau footer."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:248
msgid ""
"Adding content to an eCommerce category page helps improve the :doc:`SEO "
"<../../website/structure/seo>` strategy. Using keywords linked to the "
"products or the eCommerce categories can also increase organic traffic. "
"Additionally, each category has its own specific URL that can be pointed to "
"and is indexed by search engines."
msgstr ""
"Menambahkan konten ke halaman kategori eCommerce membantu meningkatkan "
"strategi :doc:`SEO <../../website/structure/seo>`. Menggunakan kata kunci "
"yang terkait dengan produk atau kategori eCommerce juga dapat meningkatkan "
"lalu lintas organik. Selain itu, setiap kategori memiliki URL spesifiknya "
"sendiri yang dapat ditunjuk dan diindeks oleh mesin pencari."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:252
msgid ""
"eCommerce categories can also be added as :ref:`mega menu items <website/"
"header_footer/mega-menus>` for quick access."
msgstr ""
"Kategori eCommerce juga dapat ditambahkan sebagai :ref:`item mega menu "
"<website/header_footer/mega-menus>` untuk akses cepat."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:260
msgid ""
"You can access and enable additional feature buttons such as "
"a :guilabel:`Add to cart` or :guilabel:`Wishlist` button or "
"a :guilabel:`Comparison list`. To do so, open the website editor, click the "
"desired feature buttons. All three buttons appear when hovering the mouse "
"over a product's image."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat mengakses dan mengaktifkan tombol fitur tambahan seperti tombol "
":guilabel:`Add to cart` atau :guilabel:`Wishlist` atau :guilabel:`Comparison "
"list`. Untuk melakukannya, buka editor website, klik tombol fitur yang "
"diinginkan. Ketiga tombol muncul saat mengarahkan mouse ke gambar produk."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:265
msgid ""
":icon:`fa-shopping-cart` (:guilabel:`Add to cart`): adds a button "
"to :doc:`add the product to the cart <../checkout>`;"
msgstr ""
":icon:`fa-shopping-cart` (:guilabel:`Add to cart`): menambahkan tombol untuk "
":doc:`menambahkan produk ke keranjang <../checkout>`;"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:267
msgid ""
":icon:`fa-exchange` (:guilabel:`Compare`): adds a button to compare products "
"based on their price, variant, etc.;"
msgstr ""
":icon:`fa-exchange` (:guilabel:`Compare`): menambahkan tombol untuk "
"membandingkan produk berdasarkan harga, varian, dll.;"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:269
msgid ""
":icon:`fa-heart-o` (:guilabel:`Wishlist`): adds a button to :ref:`wishlist "
"<ecommerce/products/wishlists>` the product."
msgstr ""
":icon:`fa-heart-o` (:guilabel:`Wishlist`): menambahkan tombol untuk "
":ref:`memasukkan produk ke wishlist <ecommerce/products/wishlists>`."

