msgid ""
"Then, add the alias domain as your *own domain* by clicking :guilabel:`Use "
"my own domain`, entering the alias domain (e.g., "
"`subdomain.yourdomain.com`), clicking :guilabel:`Verify`, and "
"then :guilabel:`I confirm, it's done`."
msgstr ""
"Kemudian, tambahkan domain alias sebagai *domain Anda sendiri* dengan "
"mengklik :guilabel:`Use my own domain`, memasukkan domain alias (misalnya, "
"`subdomain.yourdomain.com`), mengklik :guilabel:`Verify`, lalu :guilabel:`I "
"confirm, it's done`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:120
msgid ""
"Finally, go to your database and open the :guilabel:`Settings`. Under "
"the :guilabel:`Alias Domain` field, enter the alias domain (e.g., "
"`subdomain.yourdomain.com`), click :guilabel:`Create`, and "
"then :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Terakhir, buka database Anda dan buka :guilabel:`Settings`. Di bawah kolom "
":guilabel:`Alias Domain`, masukkan domain alias (misalnya, "
"`subdomain.yourdomain.com`), klik :guilabel:`Create`, lalu :guilabel:`Save`."

