"different :ref:`Theme styles <website/themes/theme-"
"colors>`, :guilabel:`Custom` color options, and :guilabel:`Gradient` ones."
msgstr ""
"Pilih pengaturan :guilabel:`Background` untuk mengubah palet warna melalui "
"berbagai :ref:`Theme styles <website/themes/theme-colors>`, opsi warna "
