#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/header_footer.rst:190
msgid "Add a :guilabel:`Scroll Top Button` and choose its position."
msgstr "Tambahkan :guilabel:`Scroll Top Button` dan pilih posisinya."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/header_footer.rst:191
msgid ""
"Hide or show the footer by toggling the :guilabel:`Page visibility` switch."
msgstr ""
"Sembunyikan atau tampilkan footer dengan mengaktifkan tombol :guilabel:`Page "
"visibility`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:7
msgid ""
"Odoo allows you to create pages for your website and customize their content "
"and appearance to your needs."
msgstr ""
"Odoo memungkinkan Anda membuat halaman untuk website Anda dan menyesuaikan "
"konten serta tampilannya sesuai kebutuhan Anda."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:12
msgid ""
"**Static** pages, such as the homepage or any :ref:`custom-created <website/"
"pages/page_creation>`, contain fixed content that does not change "
"dynamically. You can manually create these pages, define their URLs, and "
"adapt their :ref:`properties <website/pages/page_management>` as needed. "
"**Dynamic** pages, on the other hand, are generated dynamically. All pages "
"generated automatically by Odoo, for example, when you install an app or "
"module (e.g., `/shop` or `/blog`) or publish a new product or :doc:`blog "
"post <../../blog>`, are dynamic pages and are therefore managed differently."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:22
msgid "Page creation"
msgstr "Pembuatan halaman"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:24
msgid ""
"Website pages can be created from the **frontend** and the **backend**. To "
"create a new website page, proceed as follows:"
msgstr ""
"Halaman website dapat dibuat dari **frontend** dan **backend**. Untuk "
"membuat halaman website baru, lakukan langkah berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:27
msgid ""
"Either open the **Website** app, click :guilabel:`+ New` in the top-right "
"corner, then select :guilabel:`Page`;"
msgstr ""
"Buka aplikasi **Website**, klik :guilabel:`+ New` di sudut kanan atas, lalu "
"pilih :guilabel:`Page`;"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:29
msgid ""
"Or go to :menuselection:`Website --> Site --> Pages` and "
"click :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr ""
"Atau buka :menuselection:`Website --> Site --> Pages` dan klik "
":guilabel:`New`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:30
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`New Page` selection menu, click on a template. They are "
"sorted by type:"
msgstr ""
"Di menu pilihan :guilabel:`New Page`, klik pada template. Template diurutkan "
"berdasarkan jenis:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:32
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Basic`: Multi-purpose page. A blank page is also available to "
"start from scratch."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Basic`: Halaman multi-fungsi. Halaman kosong juga tersedia untuk "
"memulai dari awal."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:33
msgid ":guilabel:`About`: Information about your brand."
msgstr ":guilabel:`About`: Informasi tentang merek Anda."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:34
msgid ":guilabel:`Landing Pages`: Summary of company content and info."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Landing Pages`: Ringkasan konten dan info perusahaan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:35
msgid ":guilabel:`Gallery`: Photos and media showcase."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Galeri`: Tampilan foto dan media."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:36
msgid ":guilabel:`Services`: Focus on what you're selling and contact."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Services`: Fokus pada apa yang Anda jual dan kontak."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:37
msgid ":guilabel:`Pricing Plans`: Highlight on subscription and prices."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Pricing Plans`: Sorot langganan dan harga."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:38
msgid ":guilabel:`Team`: The people behind your company."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Team`: Orang-orang di balik perusahaan Anda."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:39
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Custom`: To select a custom template. To add a template to this "
"category, open the page you want to save as a template, then go "
"to :menuselection:`Site --> Properties`, enter the :guilabel:`Page "
"Title`, :ref:`edit the page's properties <website/pages/page_properties>`, "
"enable :guilabel:`Is a template`, and click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Custom`: Untuk memilih template kustom. Untuk menambahkan "
"template ke kategori ini, buka halaman yang ingin Anda simpan sebagai "
"template, lalu buka :menuselection:`Site --> Properties`, masukkan "
":guilabel:`Page Title`, :ref:`edit the page's properties <website/pages/"
"page_properties>`, aktifkan :guilabel:`Is a template`, lalu klik "
":guilabel:`Save`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:45
msgid ""
"Enter a :guilabel:`Page Title`; this title is used in the menu and the "
"page's URL."
msgstr ""
"Masukkan :guilabel:`Page Title`; judul ini digunakan dalam menu dan URL "
"halaman."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:47
msgid ""
"If needed, :doc:`customize the page's content and appearance <../"
"web_design>` using the website editor, then click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:49
msgid ":ref:`Publish <website/pages/un-publish-page>` the page."
msgstr ":ref:`Publish <website/pages/un-publish-page>` halaman."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:52
msgid ""
"Disable :guilabel:`Add to menu` if the page should not appear in the menu."
msgstr ""
"Nonaktifkan :guilabel:`Add to menu` jika halaman tidak perlu muncul di menu."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:57
msgid "Page management"
msgstr "Pengelolaan halaman"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:62
msgid "Publishing/unpublishing pages"
msgstr "Mempublikasikan/membatalkan publikasi halaman"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:64
msgid ""
"Pages need to be published to make them visible to website visitors. To "
"publish or unpublish a page, access it and toggle the switch in the upper-"
"right corner from :guilabel:`Unpublished` to :guilabel:`Published`, or vice "
"versa."
msgstr ""
"Halaman perlu dipublikasikan agar terlihat oleh pengunjung website. Untuk "
"mempublikasikan atau membatalkan publikasi halaman, akses halaman tersebut "
"dan alihkan tombol di pojok kanan atas dari :guilabel:`Unpublished` ke "
":guilabel:`Published`, atau sebaliknya."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:None
msgid "Unpublished/Published toggle"
msgstr "Tombol Unpublished/Published"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:72
msgid "It is also possible to:"
msgstr "Anda juga dapat:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:74
msgid ""
"Publish/unpublish a page from the :ref:`page properties <website/pages/"
"page_properties>`, where you can define a publishing date and/or restrict "
"the page's visibility if needed;"
msgstr ""
"Publikasikan/batalkan publikasi halaman dari :ref:`page properties <website/"
"pages/page_properties>`, di mana Anda dapat menentukan tanggal publikasi dan/"
"atau membatasi visibilitas halaman jika diperlukan;"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:76
msgid ""
"Publish/unpublish several pages at once: go to :menuselection:`Website --> "
"Site --> Pages`, select the pages, then click :guilabel:`Action` and "
"select :guilabel:`Publish` or :guilabel:`Unpublish`."
msgstr ""
"Publikasikan/batalkan publikasi beberapa halaman sekaligus: buka "
":menuselection:`Website --> Site --> Pages`, pilih halaman-halaman tersebut, "
"lalu klik :guilabel:`Action` dan pilih :guilabel:`Publish` atau "
":guilabel:`Unpublish`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:81
msgid ""
"Alternatively, you can define any :ref:`static page <website/pages/"
"page_type>` as your homepage by going to :menuselection:`Website --> Site --"
"> Properties`. Select the :guilabel:`Publish` tab and enable :guilabel:`Use "
"as Homepage`."
msgstr ""
"Sebagai alternatif, Anda dapat menetapkan :ref:`static page <website/pages/"
"page_type>` apa pun sebagai beranda Anda dengan membuka "
":menuselection:`Website --> Site --> Properties`. Pilih tab "
":guilabel:`Publish` dan aktifkan :guilabel:`Use as Homepage`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:88
msgid "Page properties"
msgstr "Properti halaman"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:90
msgid ""
"To modify a :ref:`static page's <website/pages/page_type>` properties, "
"access the page you wish to modify, then go to :menuselection:`Site --> "
"Properties`, where you can change the following properties:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengubah properti :ref:`static page's <website/pages/page_type>`, "
"akses halaman yang ingin Anda ubah, lalu buka :menuselection:`Site --> "
"Properties`, di mana Anda dapat mengubah properti berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:94
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Page URL` : Modify the page URL in the field. In this case, you "
"can redirect the old URL to the new one if needed. To do so, "
"enable :guilabel:`Redirect old URL`, then select the :guilabel:`Type` "
"of :ref:`redirection <website/pages/URL-redirection>`:"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Page URL`: Ubah URL halaman di kolom. Dalam hal ini, Anda dapat "
"mengalihkan URL lama ke yang baru jika diperlukan. Untuk melakukannya, "
"aktifkan :guilabel:`Redirect old URL`, lalu pilih :guilabel:`Type` dari "
":ref:`redirection <website/pages/URL-redirection>`:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:98
msgid ":guilabel:`301 Moved permanently`: to redirect the page permanently."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`301 Moved permanently`: untuk mengalihkan halaman secara permanen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:99
msgid ":guilabel:`302 Moved temporarily`: to redirect the page temporarily."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`302 Moved temporarily`: untuk mengalihkan halaman secara "
"sementara."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:0
msgid "Redirect old URL"
msgstr "Alihkan URL lama"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:104
msgid ""
":guilabel:`In Menu`: Disable if you don't want the page to appear in the "
"menu."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Di Menu`: Nonaktifkan jika Anda tidak ingin halaman muncul di "
"menu."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:105
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Is Homepage`: Enable if you want the page to be the homepage of "
"your website."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Adalah Beranda`: Aktifkan jika Anda ingin halaman menjadi beranda "
"website Anda."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:106
msgid ":guilabel:`Published`: Enable to publish the page."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Dipublikasikan`: Aktifkan untuk mempublikasikan halaman."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:107
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Publishing Date`: To publish the page at a specific date and "
"time, click the field, set the date and time, then press **Enter** or "
"click :guilabel:`Apply` to validate your selection."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tanggal Publikasi`: Untuk mempublikasikan halaman pada tanggal "
"dan waktu tertentu, klik bidang, atur tanggal dan waktu, lalu tekan "
"**Enter** atau klik :guilabel:`Terapkan` untuk memvalidasi pilihan Anda."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:109
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Indexed`: Disable if you don't want the page to appear in search "
"engine results."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Terindeks`: Nonaktifkan jika Anda tidak ingin halaman muncul di "
"hasil mesin pencari."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:110
msgid ":guilabel:`Visibility`: Select who can access the page:"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Visibility`: Pilih siapa yang dapat mengakses halaman:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:112
msgid ":guilabel:`Public`: Everyone can access the page."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Public`: Semua orang dapat mengakses halaman."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:113
msgid ":guilabel:`Signed In`: Only signed-in users can access the page."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Signed In`: Hanya pengguna yang masuk dapat mengakses halaman."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:114
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Restricted Group`: Select the :doc:`user access group(s) </"
"applications/general/users/access_rights>` in the :guilabel:`Authorized "
"group` field."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Grup Terbatas`: Pilih :doc:`grup akses user </applications/"
"general/users/access_rights>` di bidang :guilabel:`Grup yang Diotorisasi`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:116
msgid ""
":guilabel:`With Password`: Type the password required to access the page in "
"the :guilabel:`Password` field."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`With Password`: Ketik kata sandi yang diperlukan untuk mengakses "
"halaman di kolom :guilabel:`Password`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:119
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Is a template`: Toggle the switch to save the page as a template "
"and add it to the :guilabel:`Custom`  category."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Adalah template`: Alihkan sakelar untuk menyimpan halaman sebagai "
"template dan menambahkannya ke kategori :guilabel:`Kustom`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:123
msgid ""
"*Some* of these properties can also be modified in batch "
"from :menuselection:`Website --> Site --> Pages`."
msgstr ""
"*Beberapa* properti ini juga dapat dimodifikasi secara massal dari "
":menuselection:`Website --> Site --> Pages`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:129
msgid "Duplicating pages"
msgstr "Menduplikasi halaman"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:131
msgid ""
"To duplicate a page, access the page, then go to :menuselection:`Site --> "
"Properties`, and click :guilabel:`Duplicate Page`. Enter a :guilabel:`Page "
"Name`, then click :guilabel:`OK`. By default, the new page is added after "
"the duplicated page in the menu, but you can remove it from the menu or "
"change its position using the :doc:`menu editor <header_footer>`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:139
msgid "Deleting pages"
msgstr "Menghapus halaman"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:141
msgid "To delete a page, proceed as follows:"
msgstr "Untuk menghapus halaman, lakukan langkah berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:143
msgid ""
"Access the page, then go to :menuselection:`Site --> Properties` and "
"click :guilabel:`Delete Page`."
msgstr ""
"Akses halaman, lalu buka :menuselection:`Site --> Properties` dan klik "
":guilabel:`Hapus Halaman`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:144
msgid ""
"A pop-up window shows all links referring to the page you want to delete, "
"organized by category. To ensure website visitors don't land on an error "
"page, you must update all the links on your website referring to the page. "
"To do so, expand a category, then click on a link to open it in a new "
"window. Alternatively, you can set up a :ref:`redirection <website/pages/URL-"
"redirection>` for the deleted page."
msgstr ""
"Jendela pop-up menampilkan semua tautan yang merujuk ke halaman yang ingin "
"Anda hapus, diatur berdasarkan kategori. Untuk memastikan pengunjung website "
"tidak mendarat di halaman error, Anda harus memperbarui semua tautan di "
"website Anda yang merujuk ke halaman tersebut. Untuk melakukannya, perluas "
"kategori, lalu klik tautan untuk membukanya di jendela baru. Sebagai "
"alternatif, Anda dapat menyiapkan :ref:`pengalihan <website/pages/URL-"
"redirection>` untuk halaman yang dihapus."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:149
msgid ""
"Once you have updated the links (or set up a :ref:`redirection <website/"
"pages/URL-redirection>`), tick the :guilabel:`I am sure about this` check "
"box, then click :guilabel:`OK`."
msgstr ""
"Setelah Anda memperbarui tautan (atau menyiapkan :ref:`pengalihan <website/"
"pages/URL-redirection>`), centang kotak :guilabel:`Saya yakin tentang ini`, "
"lalu klik :guilabel:`OK`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:155
msgid "URL redirect mapping"
msgstr "Pemetaan pengalihan URL"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:157
msgid ""
"URL redirect mapping consists in sending visitors and search engines to a "
"URL different from the one they initially requested. This technique is used, "
"for example, to prevent broken links when you :ref:`delete a page <website/"
"pages/delete-page>`, :ref:`modify its URL <website/pages/page_properties>`, "
"or migrate your site from another platform to an Odoo :doc:`domain <../"
"configuration/domain_names>`. It can also be used to improve :doc:`seo`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:163
msgid ""
"To access existing URL redirections and create new ones, :doc:`activate the "
"developer mode </applications/general/developer_mode>` and go "
"to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Redirects`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengakses pengalihan URL yang ada dan membuat yang baru, "
":doc:`aktifkan mode pengembang </applications/general/developer_mode>` dan "
"buka :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Redirects`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:168
msgid ""
"A redirect record is added automatically every time you :ref:`modify a "
"page's URL <website/pages/page_properties>` and enable :guilabel:`Redirect "
"Old URL`."
msgstr ""
"Rekaman pengalihan ditambahkan secara otomatis setiap kali Anda "
":ref:`mengubah URL halaman <website/pages/page_properties>` dan mengaktifkan "
":guilabel:`Redirect Old URL`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:170
msgid ""
"You can set up redirections for :ref:`static and dynamic pages <website/"
"pages/page_type>`."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat menyiapkan pengalihan untuk :ref:`halaman statis dan dinamis "
"<website/pages/page_type>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:172
msgid ""
"To create a new redirection, click the :guilabel:`New` button, then fill in "
"the fields:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat pengalihan baru, klik tombol :guilabel:`Baru`, lalu isi bidang-"
"bidang berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:174
msgid ":guilabel:`Name`: Enter a name to identify the redirect."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Name`: Masukkan nama untuk mengidentifikasi pengalihan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:175
msgid ":guilabel:`Action`: Select the type of redirection:"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Action`: Pilih jenis pengalihan:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:177
msgid ""
":guilabel:`404 Not found`: visitors are redirected to a 404 error page when "
"they try to access an unpublished or deleted page."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`404 Not found`: pengunjung dialihkan ke halaman error 404 ketika "
"mereka mencoba mengakses halaman yang tidak dipublikasikan atau dihapus."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:179
msgid ""
":guilabel:`301 Moved Permanently`: for permanent redirections of unpublished "
"or deleted :ref:`static pages <website/pages/page_type>`. The new URL is "
"shown in search engine results, and the redirect is cached by browsers."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`301 Moved Permanently`: untuk pengalihan permanen dari "
":ref:`halaman statis <website/pages/page_type>` yang tidak dipublikasikan "
"atau dihapus. URL baru ditampilkan di hasil mesin pencari, dan pengalihan di-"
"cache oleh browser."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:182
msgid ""
":guilabel:`302 Moved Temporarily`: for short-term redirections, for example, "
"if you are redesigning or updating a page. The new URL is neither cached by "
"browsers nor shown in search engine results."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`302 Moved Temporarily`: untuk pengalihan jangka pendek, misalnya, "
"jika Anda mendesain ulang atau memperbarui halaman. URL baru tidak di-cache "
"oleh browser maupun ditampilkan di hasil mesin pencari."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:185
msgid ""
":guilabel:`308 Redirect/Rewrite`: for permanent redirections of "
"existing :ref:`dynamic pages <website/pages/page_type>`. The URL is renamed; "
"the new name is shown in search engine results and is cached by browsers. "
"Use this redirect type to rename a dynamic page, for example, if you wish to "
"rename `/shop` into `/market`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`308 Redirect/Rewrite`: untuk pengalihan permanen dari "
":ref:`halaman dinamis <website/pages/page_type>` yang ada. URL diganti "
"namanya; nama baru ditampilkan di hasil mesin pencari dan di-cache oleh "
"browser. Gunakan jenis pengalihan ini untuk mengganti nama halaman dinamis, "
"misalnya, jika Anda ingin mengganti nama `/shop` menjadi `/market`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:190
msgid ""
":guilabel:`URL from`: Enter the URL to be redirected (e.g., `/about-the-"
"company`) or search for the desired :ref:`dynamic page <website/pages/"
"page_type>` and select it from the list."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`URL from`: Masukkan URL yang akan dialihkan (misalnya, `/about-"
"the-company`) atau cari :ref:`halaman dinamis <website/pages/page_type>` "
"yang diinginkan dan pilih dari daftar."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:192
msgid ""
":guilabel:`URL to`: For 301, 302, and 308 redirects, enter the URL to be "
"redirected to. If you want to redirect to an external URL, include the "
"protocol (e.g., `https://`)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`URL to`: Untuk pengalihan 301, 302, dan 308, masukkan URL tujuan "
"pengalihan. Jika Anda ingin mengalihkan ke URL eksternal, sertakan protokol "
"(misalnya, `https://`)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:194
msgid ":guilabel:`Website`: Select a specific website."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Website`: Pilih website tertentu."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:195
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Sequence`: To define the order in which redirections are "
"performed, e.g., in the case of redirect chains (i.e., a series of redirects "
"where one URL is redirected to another one, which is itself further "
"redirected to another URL)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Sequence`: Untuk menentukan urutan pengalihan yang dilakukan, "
"misalnya dalam kasus rantai pengalihan (yaitu serangkaian pengalihan di mana "
"satu URL dialihkan ke URL lain, yang kemudian dialihkan lagi ke URL lainnya)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:199
msgid "Toggle the :guilabel:`Activate` switch to deactivate the redirection."
msgstr "Alihkan sakelar :guilabel:`Aktifkan` untuk menonaktifkan pengalihan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:202
msgid ""
"404, 301, and 302 redirections are meant to migrate traffic "
"from :ref:`unpublished <website/pages/un-publish-page>` or :ref:`deleted "
"<website/pages/delete-page>` pages to *new* pages, while the 308 redirect is "
"used for *permanent* redirections of *existing* pages."
msgstr ""
"Pengalihan 404, 301, dan 302 dimaksudkan untuk memigrasikan lalu lintas dari "
"halaman yang :ref:`tidak dipublikasikan <website/pages/un-publish-page>` "
"atau :ref:`dihapus <website/pages/delete-page>` ke halaman *baru*, sedangkan "
"pengalihan 308 digunakan untuk pengalihan *permanen* dari halaman yang *ada*."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:207
msgid ""
"`Google documentation on redirects and search <https://developers.google.com/"
"search/docs/crawling-indexing/301-redirects>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Dokumentasi Google tentang pengalihan dan pencarian <https://"
"developers.google.com/search/docs/crawling-indexing/301-redirects>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:208
msgid ":doc:`seo`"
msgstr ":doc:`seo`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:5
msgid ""
"Search Engine Optimization, often abbreviated as SEO, is a digital marketing "
"strategy to improve a website's visibility and ranking in search engine "
"results (e.g., in Google). It involves optimizing various elements on your "
"website, including its content, social sharing, URLs, images, and page speed."
msgstr ""
"Optimasi Mesin Pencari, sering disingkat sebagai SEO, adalah strategi "
"pemasaran digital untuk meningkatkan visibilitas dan peringkat website di "
"hasil mesin pencari (misalnya di Google). Ini melibatkan optimasi berbagai "
"elemen di website Anda, termasuk konten, pembagian sosial, URL, gambar, dan "
"kecepatan halaman."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:11
msgid ""
"Odoo provides several modules to help you build your website content, such "
"as :doc:`eCommerce <../../ecommerce>`, :doc:`Blog <../../"
"blog>`, :doc:`eLearning <../../elearning>`, and :doc:`Forum <../../forum>`."
msgstr ""
"Odoo menyediakan beberapa modul untuk membantu Anda membangun konten "
"website, seperti :doc:`eCommerce <../../ecommerce>`, :doc:`Blog <../../blog>"
"`, :doc:`eLearning <../../elearning>`, dan :doc:`Forum <../../forum>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:14
msgid ""
"All Odoo :doc:`themes <../web_design/themes>` rely on the CSS Framework "
"`Bootstrap <https://getbootstrap.com/>`_ to render efficiently according to "
"the device: desktop, tablet, or mobile, which positively impacts ranking in "
"search engines."
msgstr ""
"Semua :doc:`tema <../web_design/themes>` Odoo mengandalkan Framework CSS "
"`Bootstrap <https://getbootstrap.com/>`_ untuk merender secara efisien "
"sesuai dengan perangkat: desktop, tablet, atau mobile, yang berdampak "
"positif pada peringkat di mesin pencari."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:19
msgid ""
"`Magic Sheet - Optimize your website [PDF] <https://drive.google.com/drive/"
"folders/1Ywip4tWF2DPkcBaEbeXJxIZg2CjkwKgb>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Magic Sheet - Optimalkan website Anda [PDF] <https://drive.google.com/drive/"
"folders/1Ywip4tWF2DPkcBaEbeXJxIZg2CjkwKgb>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:23
msgid "Content optimization"
msgstr "Optimasi konten"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:25
msgid ""
"To optimize a webpage's SEO, access the page, then go "
"to :menuselection:`Website --> Site --> Optimize SEO`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengoptimalkan SEO halaman web, akses halaman tersebut, lalu buka "
":menuselection:`Website --> Site --> Optimize SEO`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:None
msgid "Optimize SEO"
msgstr "Optimalkan SEO"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:32
msgid ""
"If you change the title of a blog post or the name of a product, the link to "
"the related webpage is automatically updated. The old link still functions "
"as Odoo creates a :ref:`301 redirect <website/pages/URL-redirection>`, "
"maintaining the SEO."
msgstr ""
"Jika Anda mengubah judul postingan blog atau nama produk, tautan ke halaman "
"web terkait akan diperbarui secara otomatis. Tautan lama masih berfungsi "
"karena Odoo membuat :ref:`pengalihan 301 <website/pages/URL-redirection>`, "
"mempertahankan SEO."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:37
msgid "Keywords and Meta tags"
msgstr "Kata kunci dan tag Meta"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:39
msgid "There are two types of keywords in SEO, which serve different purposes."
msgstr "Ada dua jenis kata kunci dalam SEO, yang memiliki tujuan berbeda."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:42
msgid "In-text keywords"
msgstr "Kata kunci dalam teks"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:44
msgid ""
"In-text keywords appear naturally throughout a page’s visible content "
"(titles, headings, and body text) and help search engines determine the "
"topic and relevance of the page. These keywords have a real impact on "
"ranking. They cannot be edited in the :guilabel:`optimize SEO` pop-up."
msgstr ""
"Kata kunci dalam teks muncul secara alami di seluruh konten yang terlihat "
"pada halaman (judul, heading, dan teks isi) dan membantu mesin pencari "
"menentukan topik dan relevansi halaman tersebut. Kata kunci ini memiliki "
"dampak nyata pada peringkat. Kata kunci tersebut tidak dapat diedit dalam "
"pop-up :guilabel:`optimalkan SEO`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:49
msgid "It is strongly recommended to only use one H1 title per page for SEO."
msgstr ""
"Sangat disarankan untuk hanya menggunakan satu judul H1 per halaman untuk "
"SEO."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:52
msgid "Meta tags and meta keywords"
msgstr "Tag meta dan kata kunci meta"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:54
msgid ""
"**Meta tags** are HTML elements that provide information about a webpage to "
"search engines and website visitors. They play a crucial role in SEO by "
"helping search engines understand the content and context of a webpage and "
"attract visitors with appealing content. They can be edited in "
"the :guilabel:`optimize SEO` pop-up. There are two types of meta tags in "
"Odoo:"
msgstr ""
"**Tag meta** adalah elemen HTML yang memberikan informasi tentang halaman "
"web kepada mesin pencari dan pengunjung website. Tag meta memainkan peran "
"penting dalam SEO dengan membantu mesin pencari memahami konten dan konteks "
"halaman web serta menarik pengunjung dengan konten yang menarik. Tag meta "
"dapat diedit dalam pop-up :guilabel:`optimalkan SEO`. Ada dua jenis tag meta "
"di Odoo:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:59
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Title` tags specify a webpage's title and are displayed as a "
"clickable link in search engine results. They should be concise, "
"descriptive, and relevant to the page's content. You can update the title "
"tag of your webpage or keep it empty to use the default value based on the "
"page’s content."
msgstr ""
"Tag :guilabel:`Title` menentukan judul halaman web dan ditampilkan sebagai "
"tautan yang dapat diklik di hasil mesin pencari. Tag ini harus ringkas, "
"deskriptif, dan relevan dengan konten halaman. Anda dapat memperbarui tag "
"judul halaman web Anda atau membiarkannya kosong untuk menggunakan nilai "
"default berdasarkan konten halaman."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:64
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Description` tags summarize the webpage's content, often "
"displayed in search engine results below the title. They are used to "
"encourage the user to visit the page. You can update the description tag of "
"your webpage or keep it empty to use the default value based on the page’s "
"content."
msgstr ""
"Tag :guilabel:`Description` merangkum konten halaman web, sering ditampilkan "
"dalam hasil mesin pencari di bawah judul. Tag ini digunakan untuk mendorong "
"user mengunjungi halaman. Anda dapat memperbarui tag deskripsi halaman web "
"Anda atau membiarkannya kosong untuk menggunakan nilai default berdasarkan "
"konten halaman."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:70
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Preview` card displays how the title and description tags "
"should appear in search results. It also includes the URL of your page."
msgstr ""
"Kartu :guilabel:`Preview` menampilkan bagaimana tag judul dan deskripsi akan "
"muncul di hasil pencarian. Kartu ini juga mencakup URL halaman Anda."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:73
msgid ""
"**Meta keywords** are placed in a hidden HTML tag `<meta "
"name=\"keywords\">`. Once used to describe a page’s topic, this tag is now "
"ignored by major search engines and has little or no impact on SEO. To "
"edit :guilabel:`Keywords`, enter the keywords you consider essential in this "
"field and click :guilabel:`Add` to see how they are used at different levels "
"in your content (H1, H2, page title, page description, page content) and the "
"related searches in Google. The tool also suggests relevant keywords."
msgstr ""
"**Kata kunci meta** ditempatkan dalam tag HTML tersembunyi `<meta "
"name=\"keywords\">`. Tag yang dulunya digunakan untuk mendeskripsikan topik "
"halaman ini kini diabaikan oleh mesin pencari utama dan memiliki dampak yang "
"kecil atau tidak ada sama sekali pada SEO. Untuk mengedit :guilabel:`Kata "
"Kunci`, masukkan kata kunci yang Anda anggap penting di bidang ini dan klik "
":guilabel:`Tambah` untuk melihat bagaimana kata kunci tersebut digunakan "
"pada berbagai tingkat dalam konten Anda (H1, H2, judul halaman, deskripsi "
"halaman, konten halaman) dan pencarian terkait di Google. Alat ini juga "
"menyarankan kata kunci yang relevan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:81
#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:64
msgid "Images"
msgstr "Gambar"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:83
msgid ""
"The size of images has a significant impact on page speed, which is an "
"essential criterion for search engines to optimize SEO ranking."
msgstr ""
"Ukuran gambar memiliki dampak signifikan pada kecepatan halaman, yang "
"merupakan kriteria penting bagi mesin pencari untuk mengoptimalkan peringkat "
"SEO."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:87
msgid ""
"Compare how your website ranks using `Google Page Speed <https://"
"pagespeed.web.dev/?utm_source=psi&utm_medium=redirect>`_ or `Pingdom Website "
"Speed Test <https://tools.pingdom.com/>`_."
msgstr ""
"Bandingkan bagaimana peringkat website Anda menggunakan `Google Page Speed "
"<https://pagespeed.web.dev/?utm_source=psi&utm_medium=redirect>`_ atau "
"`Pingdom Website Speed Test <https://tools.pingdom.com/>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:90
msgid ""
"Odoo automatically compresses uploaded images and converts them to `Webp`. "
"With this file format, photos are smaller, which increases the page loading "
"speed and, therefore, gives a better ranking in SEO. All images used in Odoo "
"official :doc:`themes <../web_design/themes>` are also compressed by "
"default. If you are using a third-party theme, it may provide images that "
"are not compressed efficiently."
msgstr ""
"Odoo secara otomatis mengompresi gambar yang diunggah dan mengonversinya ke "
"`Webp`. Dengan format file ini, foto menjadi lebih kecil, yang meningkatkan "
"kecepatan pemuatan halaman dan, oleh karena itu, memberikan peringkat yang "
"lebih baik dalam SEO. Semua gambar yang digunakan dalam :doc:`tema <../"
"web_design/themes>` resmi Odoo juga dikompres secara default. Jika Anda "
"menggunakan tema pihak ketiga, tema tersebut mungkin menyediakan gambar yang "
"tidak dikompres secara efisien."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:96
msgid ""
"**To modify an image** from your website, select the image, "
"click :guilabel:`Edit`, then go to the :guilabel:`Customize` tab, and adapt "
"the :guilabel:`Format` in the :guilabel:`Image` section."
msgstr ""
"**Untuk mengubah gambar** dari website Anda, pilih gambar, klik "
":guilabel:`Edit`, lalu buka tab :guilabel:`Customize`, dan sesuaikan "
":guilabel:`Format` di bagian :guilabel:`Image`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:100
msgid ""
"Alt tags are used to provide context to what an image is displaying, "
"informing search engine crawlers and allowing them to index an image "
"correctly. Adding alt tags keywords in the :guilabel:`Description` field is "
"essential from an SEO perspective. This description is added to the HTML "
"code of your image, and it is shown when the image cannot be displayed."
msgstr ""
"Tag alt digunakan untuk memberikan konteks tentang apa yang ditampilkan "
"gambar, memberi informasi kepada crawler mesin pencari dan memungkinkan "
"mereka mengindeks gambar dengan benar. Menambahkan kata kunci tag alt di "
"kolom :guilabel:`Description` sangat penting dari perspektif SEO. Deskripsi "
"ini ditambahkan ke kode HTML gambar Anda, dan ditampilkan ketika gambar "
"tidak dapat ditampilkan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:106
msgid "Image for social share"
msgstr "Gambar untuk pembagian sosial"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:108
msgid ""
"When you share your page on social media, your website logo is selected by "
"default, but you can search the :doc:`Unsplash image library <../../../"
"general/integrations/unsplash>` or upload any other image by clicking "
"the :icon:`fa-upload` :guilabel:`(upload)` button."
msgstr ""
"Ketika Anda membagikan halaman Anda di media sosial, logo website Anda "
"dipilih secara default, tetapi Anda dapat mencari :doc:`Perpustakaan gambar "
"Unsplash <../../../general/integrations/unsplash>` atau mengunggah gambar "
"lain dengan mengklik tombol :icon:`fa-upload` :guilabel:`unggah`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:113
msgid ""
"You can set a default social share image. Go to :menuselection:`Website --> "
"Configuration --> Settings` in the :guilabel:`SEO` section and tick "
"the :guilabel:`Default Social Share Image` checkbox."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat mengatur gambar berbagi sosial default. Buka "
":menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings` di bagian "
":guilabel:`SEO` dan centang kotak :guilabel:`Default Social Share Image`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:117
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Social Preview` card displays how the page's information "
"would appear when shared."
msgstr ""
"Kartu :guilabel:`Social Preview` menampilkan bagaimana informasi halaman "
"akan muncul saat dibagikan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:121
msgid "Indexation"
msgstr "Pengindeksan"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:123
msgid ""
"Website indexation is the process by which search engines, such as Google, "
"discover, analyze, and store information about a website's content in their "
"database. Search engine bots, known as crawlers or spiders, visit web pages "
"and follow links to collect data, including text, images, and other media. "
"The purpose of indexation is to make a website's content searchable and "
"discoverable to users. Without being indexed, a website or a specific page "
"on that site will not appear in search engine results, regardless of how "
"relevant or well-designed it is. Indexation is a fundamental step "
"in :abbr:`SEO (Search Engine Optimization)`, serving as the foundation for a "
"website's visibility and organic traffic."
msgstr ""
"Pengindeksan website adalah proses di mana mesin pencari, seperti Google, "
"menemukan, menganalisis, dan menyimpan informasi tentang konten website "
"dalam database mereka. Bot mesin pencari, yang dikenal sebagai crawler atau "
"spider, mengunjungi halaman web dan mengikuti tautan untuk mengumpulkan "
"data, termasuk teks, gambar, dan media lainnya. Tujuan pengindeksan adalah "
"membuat konten website dapat dicari dan ditemukan oleh pengguna. Tanpa "
"diindeks, sebuah website atau halaman tertentu di situs tersebut tidak akan "
"muncul dalam hasil mesin pencari, terlepas dari seberapa relevan atau "
"dirancang dengan baik. Pengindeksan adalah langkah mendasar dalam :abbr:`SEO "
"(Search Engine Optimization)`, berfungsi sebagai fondasi untuk visibilitas "
"website dan lalu lintas organik."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:133
msgid ""
"**When you first create your website on Odoo, it will not appear directly in "
"search engine results.** Search engines need time to crawl and index it, "
"which can take anywhere from a few days to several weeks. For Google, you "
"can use the :doc:`Search Console <../configuration/google_search_console>` "
"and request indexing for specific URLs, though this does not guarantee "
"faster results. If you have an existing website and are migrating, your "
"previous website may still appear instead of the new one during that "
"timeframe."
msgstr ""
"**Ketika Anda pertama kali membuat website di Odoo, website tersebut tidak "
"akan langsung muncul dalam hasil mesin pencari.** Mesin pencari membutuhkan "
"waktu untuk meng-crawl dan mengindeksnya, yang dapat memakan waktu dari "
"beberapa hari hingga beberapa minggu. Untuk Google, Anda dapat menggunakan "
":doc:`Search Console <../configuration/google_search_console>` dan meminta "
"pengindeksan untuk URL tertentu, meskipun ini tidak menjamin hasil yang "
"lebih cepat. Jika Anda memiliki website yang sudah ada dan sedang melakukan "
"migrasi, website lama Anda mungkin masih muncul sebagai ganti website yang "
"baru selama jangka waktu tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:141
msgid "SEO impact when migrating your existing website to Odoo"
msgstr "Dampak SEO saat memigrasikan website yang ada ke Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:143
msgid ""
"In most cases, migrating to Odoo will not negatively impact your SEO. While "
"no platform can guarantee that rankings will remain unchanged, follow these "
"best practices to significantly reduce the risk."
msgstr ""
"Dalam kebanyakan kasus, migrasi ke Odoo tidak akan berdampak negatif pada "
"SEO Anda. Meskipun tidak ada platform yang dapat menjamin bahwa peringkat "
"akan tetap tidak berubah, ikuti praktik terbaik ini untuk mengurangi risiko "
"secara signifikan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:147
msgid "Keep your existing content."
msgstr "Pertahankan konten Anda yang ada."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:149
msgid ""
"Implement :ref:`redirects <website/pages/URL-redirection>` from old URLs to "
"their new counterparts."
msgstr ""
"Terapkan :ref:`pengalihan <website/pages/URL-redirection>` dari URL lama ke "
"URL baru yang sesuai."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:151
msgid ""
"Monitor traffic and indexation to make sure that everything is going well, "
"using :doc:`../configuration/google_search_console`."
msgstr ""
"Pantau lalu lintas dan pengindeksan untuk memastikan semuanya berjalan baik, "
"menggunakan :doc:`../configuration/google_search_console`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:153
msgid ""
"By doing this, you help search engines reindex your site and maintain your "
"visibility in search results."
msgstr ""
"Dengan melakukan ini, Anda membantu mesin pencari mengindeks ulang situs "
"Anda dan mempertahankan visibilitas Anda dalam hasil pencarian."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:157
msgid "It is normal to experience a traffic decrease in the first days."
msgstr "Wajar mengalami penurunan lalu lintas di hari-hari pertama."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:160
msgid "Prevent a page from being indexed"
msgstr "Mencegah halaman diindeks"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:162
msgid ""
"To effectively prevent a page from appearing in search engine results, use "
"one of the following methods:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk secara efektif mencegah halaman muncul di hasil mesin pencari, gunakan "
"salah satu metode berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:165
msgid ""
"**noindex tag:** Access the page's :ref:`properties <website/pages/"
"page_properties>` and toggle the :guilabel:`Indexed` switch off."
msgstr ""
"**Tag noindex:** Akses :ref:`properti <website/pages/page_properties>` "
"halaman dan matikan tombol :guilabel:`Indexed`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:169
msgid ""
"This option is not yet available for :ref:`dynamic pages <website/pages/"
"page_type>`."
msgstr ""
"Opsi ini belum tersedia untuk :ref:`halaman dinamis <website/pages/page_type>"
"`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:171
msgid ""
"**404 or 403:** Configure the page to return a 404 (Not Found) or 403 "
"(Forbidden) HTTP status code. These codes signal to search engines that the "
"page does not exist or is inaccessible, leading to its eventual removal from "
"the index."
msgstr ""
"**404 atau 403:** Konfigurasi halaman untuk mengembalikan kode status HTTP "
"404 (Not Found) atau 403 (Forbidden). Kode ini memberi sinyal kepada mesin "
"pencari bahwa halaman tidak ada atau tidak dapat diakses, yang menyebabkan "
"penghapusannya dari indeks."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:175
msgid ""
"**404:** :ref:`Configure a 404 redirection. <website/pages/URL-redirection>`"
msgstr ""
"**404:** :ref:`Konfigurasi pengalihan 404. <website/pages/URL-redirection>`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:176
msgid ""
"**403:** Access the page's :ref:`properties <website/pages/page_properties>` "
"and toggle the :guilabel:`Visibility` switch off or :ref:`unpublish the page "
"<website/pages/un-publish-page>`."
msgstr ""
"**403:** Akses :ref:`properti <website/pages/page_properties>` halaman dan "
"matikan tombol :guilabel:`Visibility` atau :ref:`batalkan publikasi halaman "
"<website/pages/un-publish-page>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:179
msgid ""
"**Google Search Console:** Use Google Search Console to request the removal "
"of specific URLs from Google's index."
msgstr ""
"**Google Search Console:** Gunakan Google Search Console untuk meminta "
"penghapusan URL tertentu dari indeks Google."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:183
msgid ":doc:`../configuration/google_search_console`"
msgstr ":doc:`../configuration/google_search_console`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:184
msgid ":doc:`pages`"
msgstr ":doc:`pages`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:187
msgid "Prevent a website from being indexed"
msgstr "Mencegah website diindeks"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:189
msgid ""
"To prevent a website from appearing in search engine results, go "
"to :menuselection:`Configuration --> Settings`, then in "
"the :guilabel:`Website Info` section, add a random value in "
"the :guilabel:`Domain` field. Doing so automatically inserts the following "
"tag into the page source:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk mencegah website muncul dalam hasil mesin pencari, buka "
":menuselection:`Configuration --> Settings`, kemudian di bagian "
":guilabel:`Website Info`, tambahkan nilai acak di bidang :guilabel:`Domain`. "
"Melakukan hal ini secara otomatis menyisipkan tag berikut ke dalam sumber "
"halaman:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:198
msgid ""
"This tag instructs search engines not to index the site. After applying the "
"change, it may take several days or weeks for search engines to update their "
"results and remove the website."
msgstr ""
"Tag ini menginstruksikan mesin pencari untuk tidak mengindeks situs. Setelah "
"menerapkan perubahan, mesin pencari mungkin memerlukan beberapa hari atau "
"minggu untuk memperbarui hasil mereka dan menghapus website tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:202
msgid ""
"This can be used to prevent websites from test databases from appearing in "
"search results."
msgstr ""
"Ini dapat digunakan untuk mencegah website dari database uji muncul dalam "
"hasil pencarian."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:205
msgid "Sitemap"
msgstr "Sitemap"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:207
msgid ""
"The sitemap points out website pages and their relation to each other to "
"search engine crawlers. Odoo generates a `/sitemap.xml` file, including all "
"URLs. For performance reasons, this file is cached and updated every 12 "
"hours."
msgstr ""
"Sitemap menunjukkan halaman website dan hubungan mereka satu sama lain "
"kepada crawler mesin pencari. Odoo menghasilkan file `/sitemap.xml`, yang "
"mencakup semua URL. Untuk alasan performa, file ini di-cache dan diperbarui "
"setiap 12 jam."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:212
msgid ""
"If your website has a lot of pages, Odoo automatically creates a Sitemap "
"Index file, respecting the `sitemaps.org protocol <http://www.sitemaps.org/"
"protocol.html>`_, grouping sitemap URLs in 45000 chunks per file."
msgstr ""
"Jika website Anda memiliki banyak halaman, Odoo secara otomatis membuat file "
"Sitemap Index, sesuai dengan `protokol sitemaps.org <http://www.sitemaps.org/"
"protocol.html>`_, mengelompokkan URL sitemap dalam potongan 45000 per file."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:216
msgid ""
"Every sitemap entry has three attributes that are computed automatically:"
msgstr ""
"Setiap entri peta situs memiliki tiga atribut yang dihitung secara otomatis:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:218
msgid "`<loc>`: the URL of a page."
msgstr "`<loc>`: URL dari sebuah halaman."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:219
msgid ""
"`<lastmod>`: last modification date of the resource, computed automatically "
"based on the related object. For a page related to a product, this could be "
"the last modification date of the product or the page."
msgstr ""
"`<lastmod>`: tanggal modifikasi terakhir dari sumber daya, dihitung secara "
"otomatis berdasarkan objek terkait. Untuk halaman yang terkait dengan "
"produk, ini bisa menjadi tanggal modifikasi terakhir dari produk atau "
"halaman tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:222
msgid ""
"`<priority>`: modules may implement their priority algorithm based on their "
"content (for example, a forum might assign a priority based on the number of "
"votes on a specific post). The priority of a static page is defined by its "
"priority field, which is normalized (16 is the default)."
msgstr ""
"`<priority>`: modul dapat mengimplementasikan algoritma prioritas mereka "
"berdasarkan konten mereka (misalnya, sebuah forum mungkin menetapkan "
"prioritas berdasarkan jumlah suara pada pos tertentu). Prioritas halaman "
"statis didefinisikan oleh bidang prioritasnya, yang dinormalisasi (16 adalah "
"nilai default)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:227
msgid ""
"To prevent pages from appearing in a sitemap, go to :menuselection:`Site --> "
"Properties`, and toggle off the :guilabel:`Indexed` feature."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mencegah halaman muncul dalam sitemap, buka :menuselection:`Site --> "
"Properties`, dan nonaktifkan fitur :guilabel:`Indexed`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:0
msgid "toggle off the “Indexed” field"
msgstr "nonaktifkan bidang \"Indexed\""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:234
msgid "robots.txt"
msgstr "robots.txt"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:236
msgid ""
"A `robots.txt` file instructs search engine crawlers which parts of a "
"website they are permitted to access. Its primary purpose is to:"
msgstr ""
"File `robots.txt` menginstruksikan crawler mesin pencari bagian mana dari "
"website yang diizinkan untuk diakses. Tujuan utamanya adalah untuk:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:239
msgid ""
"**Prevent overloading the website:** By guiding crawlers away from certain "
"sections, robots.txt helps manage server load."
msgstr ""
"**Mencegah kelebihan beban pada website:** Dengan memandu crawler menjauh "
"dari bagian tertentu, robots.txt membantu mengelola beban server."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:241
msgid ""
"**Control access to resources and detailed descriptions:** It can prevent "
"crawlers from accessing media files (images, videos), CSS stylesheets, and "
"JavaScript files, and from reading the content (text) of specific pages."
msgstr ""
"**Mengontrol akses ke resource dan deskripsi detail:** File ini dapat "
"mencegah crawler mengakses file media (gambar, video), stylesheet CSS, dan "
"file JavaScript, serta membaca konten (teks) dari halaman tertentu."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:245
msgid ""
"When indexing your website, search engines first look at the robots.txt "
"file. Odoo automatically creates one robot.txt file available on "
"`mydatabase.odoo.com/robots.txt`."
msgstr ""
"Saat mengindeks website Anda, mesin pencari pertama-tama melihat file "
"robots.txt. Odoo secara otomatis membuat satu file robot.txt yang tersedia "
"di `mydatabase.odoo.com/robots.txt`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:249
msgid ""
"Reputable bots adhere to robots.txt; others may require blocking "
"via :ref:`Cloudflare <domain-name/naked/cloudflare>` on your custom domain."
msgstr ""
"Bot yang memiliki reputasi baik mematuhi robots.txt; yang lain mungkin perlu "
"diblokir melalui :ref:`Cloudflare <domain-name/naked/cloudflare>` pada "
"domain kustom Anda."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:253
msgid "Edit robots.txt"
msgstr "Edit robots.txt"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:255
msgid ""
"By editing a robots.txt file, you can control which site pages are "
"accessible to search engine crawlers. To add custom instructions to the "
"file, go to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings`, scroll "
"down to the :guilabel:`SEO` section, and click :guilabel:`Edit robots.txt`."
msgstr ""
"Dengan mengedit file robots.txt, Anda dapat mengontrol halaman situs mana "
"yang dapat diakses oleh crawler mesin pencari. Untuk menambahkan instruksi "
"khusus ke file, buka :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> "
"Settings`, gulir ke bawah ke bagian :guilabel:`SEO`, dan klik "
":guilabel:`Edit robots.txt`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:260
msgid ""
"If you do not want robots to crawl the `/about-us` page of your site, you "
"can edit the robots.txt file to add `Disallow: /about-us`."
msgstr ""
"Jika Anda tidak ingin robot meng-crawl halaman `/about-us` dari situs Anda, "
"Anda dapat mengedit file robots.txt untuk menambahkan `Disallow: /about-us`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:264
msgid ""
"While `robots.txt` prevents content from being crawled, **it does not "
"guarantee that a page will not be indexed**. A page can still appear in "
"search results if it is linked to from other crawled pages (indexed by "
"\"reference\"). Google generally does not recommend using robots.txt to "
"block webpages that you wish to keep out of search results entirely."
msgstr ""
"Meskipun `robots.txt` mencegah konten di-crawl, **file ini tidak menjamin "
"bahwa halaman tidak akan diindeks**. Halaman masih dapat muncul di hasil "
"pencarian jika ditautkan dari halaman lain yang di-crawl (diindeks "
"berdasarkan \"referensi\"). Google umumnya tidak merekomendasikan penggunaan "
"robots.txt untuk memblokir halaman web yang ingin Anda jaga agar tidak "
"muncul di hasil pencarian sepenuhnya."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:270
msgid "Advanced features"
msgstr "Fitur tingkat lanjut"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:273
msgid "Structured data markup"
msgstr "Markup data terstruktur"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:275
msgid ""
"Structured data markup is used to generate rich snippets in search engine "
"results. It is a way for websites to send structured data to search engine "
"crawlers, helping them understand your content and create well-presented "
"search results."
msgstr ""
"Markup data terstruktur digunakan untuk menghasilkan snippet kaya dalam "
"hasil mesin pencari. Ini adalah cara bagi website untuk mengirim data "
"terstruktur ke crawler mesin pencari, membantu mereka memahami konten Anda "
"dan membuat hasil pencarian yang tersaji dengan baik."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:279
msgid ""
"By default, Google supports many `rich snippets <https://"
"developers.google.com/search/blog/2009/05/introducing-rich-snippets>`_ for "
"content types, including Reviews, People, Products, Businesses, Events, and "
"Organizations."
msgstr ""
"Secara default, Google mendukung banyak `rich snippets <https://"
"developers.google.com/search/blog/2009/05/introducing-rich-snippets>`_ untuk "
"tipe konten, termasuk Ulasan, Orang, Produk, Bisnis, Acara, dan Organisasi."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:282
msgid ""
"Microdata is a set of tags, introduced with HTML5, that help search engines "
"better understand your content and display it in a relevant way. Odoo "
"implements microdata as defined in the schema.org `specification <https://"
"schema.org/docs/gs.html>`_ for events, eCommerce products, forum posts, and "
"contact addresses. This allows your product pages to be displayed in Google "
"using extra information like the price and rating of a product:"
msgstr ""
"Microdata adalah kumpulan tag, yang diperkenalkan dengan HTML5, yang "
"membantu mesin pencari memahami konten Anda dengan lebih baik dan "
"menampilkannya dengan cara yang relevan. Odoo mengimplementasikan microdata "
"sebagaimana didefinisikan dalam `spesifikasi <https://schema.org/docs/"
"gs.html>`_ schema.org untuk acara, produk eCommerce, postingan forum, dan "
"alamat kontak. Ini memungkinkan halaman produk Anda ditampilkan di Google "
"menggunakan informasi tambahan seperti harga dan rating produk:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:None
msgid "snippets in search engine results"
msgstr "snippet dalam hasil mesin pencari"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:292
msgid "Hreflang HTML tags"
msgstr "Tag HTML Hreflang"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:294
msgid ""
"Odoo automatically includes `hreflang` and `x-default` tags in the code of "
"your website's multilingual pages. These HTML attributes are crucial in "
"informing search engines about a specific page's language and geographical "
"targeting."
msgstr ""
"Odoo secara otomatis menyertakan tag `hreflang` dan `x-default` dalam kode "
"halaman multibahasa website Anda. Atribut HTML ini sangat penting dalam "
"memberi tahu mesin pencari tentang bahasa dan penargetan geografis halaman "
"tertentu."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:299
msgid ":doc:`../configuration/translate`"
msgstr ":doc:`../configuration/translate`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design.rst:9
msgid ""
"Design your website using :doc:`building blocks <../website/web_design/"
"building_blocks>`, customize its :doc:`theme <../website/web_design/themes>` "
"with various options, structure and present content with :doc:`elements <../"
"website/web_design/elements>`, and display or hide building blocks "
"using :doc:`visibility settings <../website/web_design/visibility>`."
msgstr ""
"Rancang website Anda menggunakan :doc:`blok bangunan <../website/web_design/"
"building_blocks>`, sesuaikan :doc:`tema <../website/web_design/themes>` "
"dengan berbagai opsi, strukturkan dan sajikan konten dengan :doc:`elemen <../"
"website/web_design/elements>`, serta tampilkan atau sembunyikan blok "
"bangunan menggunakan :doc:`pengaturan visibilitas <../website/web_design/"
"visibility>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design.rst:16
#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:5
msgid "Building blocks"
msgstr "Bok penyusun"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design.rst:16
msgid ""
"Design your website by dragging and dropping building blocks, then editing "
"them to fit your content and layout needs."
msgstr ""
"Rancang website Anda dengan menarik dan meletakkan blok bangunan, lalu edit "
"untuk menyesuaikan konten dan kebutuhan tata letak."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design.rst:23
#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:3
msgid "General theme"
msgstr "Tema umum"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design.rst:23
msgid ""
"Customize your website’s theme by adjusting its colors, fonts, and layout."
msgstr ""
"Sesuaikan tema website Anda dengan menyesuaikan warna, font, dan tata letak."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design.rst:29
#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:3
msgid "Elements"
msgstr "Element"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design.rst:29
msgid ""
"Structure and present content effectively with elements such as titles, "
"lists, etc."
msgstr ""
"Susun dan sajikan konten secara efektif dengan elemen seperti judul, daftar, "
"dll."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design.rst:35
#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/visibility.rst:3
msgid "Visibility"
msgstr "Visibilitas"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design.rst:35
msgid "Display or hide building blocks based on several criteria."
msgstr "Tampilkan atau sembunyikan blok bangunan berdasarkan beberapa kriteria."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:7
msgid ""
"You can design your website by :ref:`dragging and dropping building blocks "
"<website/building_blocks/add>`, then :ref:`editing them <website/"
"building_blocks/edit>` to fit your content and layout needs."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat merancang website dengan :ref:`menyeret dan melepaskan blok "
"bangunan <website/building_blocks/add>`, lalu :ref:`mengeditnya <website/"
"building_blocks/edit>` agar sesuai dengan kebutuhan konten dan tata letak "
"Anda."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:12
msgid ""
"`Odoo Tutorial: Design your website: text and colors <https://www.odoo.com/"
"slides/slide/design-your-website-text-and-colors-6930?fullscreen=1>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Tutorial Odoo: Rancang website Anda: teks dan warna <https://www.odoo.com/"
"slides/slide/design-your-website-text-and-colors-6930?fullscreen=1>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:17
msgid "Add a building block"
msgstr "Tambahkan blok bangunan"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:19
msgid ""
"To add a block to a :doc:`website page <../structure/pages>`, access the "
"page, click :guilabel:`Edit`, then drag and drop the desired building block "
"into the appropriate location. Two types of building blocks are "
"available: :guilabel:`Categories` and :guilabel:`Inner "
"Content`. :guilabel:`Inner Content` building blocks can only be added "
"into :guilabel:`Categories` building blocks."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menambahkan blok ke :doc:`halaman website <../structure/pages>`, akses "
"halaman tersebut, klik :guilabel:`Edit`, lalu seret dan lepaskan blok "
"bangunan yang diinginkan ke lokasi yang sesuai. Dua jenis blok bangunan "
"tersedia: :guilabel:`Categories` dan :guilabel:`Inner Content`. Blok "
"bangunan :guilabel:`Inner Content` hanya dapat ditambahkan ke dalam blok "
"bangunan :guilabel:`Categories`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:24
msgid ""
"When clicking on a category block, a popup appears, allowing you to select "
"between multiple templates for each category."
msgstr ""
"Saat mengklik blok kategori, popup muncul yang memungkinkan Anda memilih "
"antara beberapa template untuk setiap kategori."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:28
msgid ""
"You can also search for a specific block in the :guilabel:`Insert a block` "
"popup using the search bar."
msgstr ""
"Anda juga dapat mencari blok tertentu di popup :guilabel:`Insert a block` "
"menggunakan bilah pencarian."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:0
msgid "Pop-up block selection"
msgstr "Pemilihan blok pop-up"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:34
msgid ""
"Once the category block is placed, you can drag and drop :guilabel:`Inner "
"content` blocks within it. The :guilabel:`Inner content` blocks allow you to "
"add elements, such as videos, images, social media buttons, etc., into pre-"
"existing category blocks."
msgstr ""
"Setelah blok kategori ditempatkan, Anda dapat menyeret dan melepaskan blok "
":guilabel:`Inner content` di dalamnya. Blok :guilabel:`Inner content` "
"memungkinkan Anda menambahkan elemen, seperti video, gambar, tombol media "
"sosial, dll., ke dalam blok kategori yang sudah ada."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:39
msgid ""
"Access to certain blocks requires the installation of their respective "
"application or module (e.g., eCommerce for the :guilabel:`Products` block)."
msgstr ""
"Akses ke blok tertentu memerlukan instalasi aplikasi atau modul yang sesuai "
"(misalnya, eCommerce untuk blok :guilabel:`Products`)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:43
msgid ""
"Add all your social media accounts in one place with the inner "
"content :guilabel:`Social Media` block. Toggle the switch on or off next to "
"the desired platform and copy/paste your account URL."
msgstr ""
"Tambahkan semua akun media sosial Anda di satu tempat dengan blok inner "
"content :guilabel:`Social Media`. Aktifkan atau nonaktifkan sakelar di "
"samping platform yang diinginkan dan salin/tempel URL akun Anda."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:0
msgid "Social Media inner content block"
msgstr "Blok inner content Social Media"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:52
msgid "Form"
msgstr "Formulir"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:54
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Form` block is used to collect information from website "
"visitors and create records in your database, if applicable. To add a form "
"to a website page, drag and drop the :guilabel:`Contact & Forms` category, "
"then select the :guilabel:`Form block`."
msgstr ""
"Blok :guilabel:`Form` digunakan untuk mengumpulkan informasi dari pengunjung "
"website dan membuat record di database Anda, jika berlaku. Untuk menambahkan "
"formulir ke halaman website, seret dan lepas dari kategori "
":guilabel:`Contact & Forms`, kemudian pilih :guilabel:`Form block`."

